msgstr ":doc:`Mailjet dokumentacija <email_communication/mailjet_api>`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/email_communication.rst:85
msgid ""
"Every provider has its own limitations. Research the desired provider "
"*before* configuring it. For example, Outlook and Gmail might not be "
"suitable for large marketing campaigns."
msgstr ""
"Vsak ponudnik ima svoje omejitve. Preverite želenega ponudnika *preden* ga "
"konfigurirate. Na primer, Outlook in Gmail morda nista primerna za obsežne "
"trženjske kampanje."

