"moral samodejno odpreti in preusmeriti na :ref:`domačo stran IoT boxa <iot/"
"iot-box/homepage>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:59
msgid ""
"Depending on your operating system, the browser might not open and redirect "
"to the IoT box's homepage. In this case, open your browser manually and "
"navigate to `http://10.11.12.1` or any url starting with **http** (e.g., "
"`http://odoo.com`)."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od vašega operacijskega sistema se brskalnik morda ne bo odprl in "
"preusmeril na domačo stran IoT boxa. V tem primeru ročno odprite brskalnik "
"in pojdite na `http://10.11.12.1` ali kateri koli url, ki se začne s "
"**http** (npr. `http://odoo.com`)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:63
msgid ""
"On the IoT box's homepage, click :guilabel:`Configure` next to "
"the :guilabel:`Internet Status` section."
msgstr ""
"Na domači strani IoT boxa kliknite :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj` poleg "
"razdelka :guilabel:`Stanje interneta`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:65
msgid ""
"Wait a few minutes for the available networks to be scanned, select the "
"network, enter the Wi-Fi's password, and click :guilabel:`Connect`."
msgstr ""
"Počakajte nekaj minut, da se pregledajo razpoložljiva omrežja, izberite "
"omrežje, vnesite geslo Wi-Fi in kliknite :guilabel:`Poveži`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:69
msgid ""
"Once connected to the Wi-Fi network, the IoT box stops emitting its Wi-Fi "
"signal, and the computer should automatically reconnect to its original "
"network. If it does not, reconnect to it manually."
msgstr ""
"Ko je IoT box povezan z Wi-Fi omrežjem, preneha oddajati svoj Wi-Fi signal "
"in računalnik bi se moral samodejno ponovno povezati s svojim prvotnim "
"omrežjem. Če se ne, ga ponovno povežite ročno."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:76
msgid "IoT box homepage"
msgstr "Domača stran IoT boxa"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:78
msgid ""
"To access the IoT box's homepage, open a web browser **on the same network "
"as the IoT box** and navigate to the IoT box's IP address."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do domače strani IoT boxa odprite spletni brskalnik **v istem "
"omrežju kot IoT box** in pojdite na IP naslov IoT boxa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:None
msgid "IoT box's homepage"
msgstr "Domača stran IoT boxa"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:85
msgid "The IoT box's IP address can be retrieved by:"
msgstr "IP naslov IoT boxa lahko pridobite tako, da:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:87
msgid ""
"connecting the IoT box to an external monitor: the IP address is displayed "
"on the screen."
msgstr ""
"povezovanje IoT boxa z zunanjim monitorjem: IP naslov je prikazan na zaslonu."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:0
msgid "POS display with IoT box's IP address"
msgstr "POS zaslon z IP naslovom IoT boxa"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:93
msgid ""
"connecting the IoT box to a `supported receipt or label printer <https://"
"www.odoo.com/app/iot-hardware>`_ with a USB cable: the IP address is "
"automatically printed."
msgstr ""
"povežete IoT box s `podprtim tiskalником za račune ali nalepke <https://"
"www.odoo.com/app/iot-hardware>`_ z USB kablom: IP naslov se samodejno "
"natisne."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:95
msgid ""
"accessing the administrator interface of the router to which the IoT box is "
"connected or using third-party software to scan the network."
msgstr ""
"dostopate do skrbniškega vmesnika usmerjevalnika, na katerega je povezan IoT "
"box, ali uporabljate programsko opremo tretjih oseb za pregledovanje omrežja."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/iot_box.rst:98
msgid ""
"Once the IoT box is :doc:`connected to the Odoo database <connect>`, its "
"homepage can be accessed from Odoo by opening the IoT app and clicking the "
"URL displayed on the IoT box's card."
msgstr ""
"Ko je IoT box :doc:`povezan z bazo podatkov Odoo <connect>`, je do njegove "
"domače strani mogoče dostopati iz Odoo tako, da odprete aplikacijo IoT in "
"kliknete URL, prikazan na kartici IoT boxa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:5
msgid "To start using the Windows virtual IoT:"
msgstr "Za začetek uporabe Windows virtual IoT:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:7
msgid ""
"Make sure all :ref:`prerequisites <iot/windows-iot/prerequisites>` are met."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da so izpolnjeni vsi :ref:`predpogoji <iot/windows-iot/"
"prerequisites>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:8
msgid ""
":ref:`Install the Windows virtual IoT <iot/windows-iot/installation>` on a "
"Windows computer."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Namestite Windows virtualni IoT <iot/windows-iot/installation>` na "
"računalnik z operacijskim sistemom Windows."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:9
msgid ":ref:`Configure the Windows Firewall <iot/windows-iot/firewall>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Konfigurirajte Windows Firewall <iot/windows-iot/firewall>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:10
msgid "Connect your :doc:`devices <devices>` to the Windows virtual IoT."
msgstr "Povežite vaše :doc:`naprave <devices>` z Windows virtual IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:11
msgid ":doc:`Connect the Windows virtual IoT to your Odoo database <connect>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Povežite Windows virtual IoT z vašo Odoo bazo podatkov <connect>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:18
msgid ""
"The following prerequisites must be met before setting up and using the "
"Windows virtual IoT:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednji predpogoji morajo biti izpolnjeni pred nastavljanjem in uporabo "
"Windows virtualnega IoT:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:20
msgid "A valid :ref:`IoT box subscription <iot/iot/iot-subscription>`."
msgstr "Veljavna :ref:`naročnina na IoT box <iot/iot/iot-subscription>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:21
msgid ""
"An updated and recent version of Windows (i.e., Windows 10 or Windows 11) "
"installed on a Windows computer (laptop, desktop, or server)."
msgstr ""
"Posodobljena in novejša različica operacijskega sistema Windows (tj. Windows "
"10 ali Windows 11), nameščena na računalniku z Windows (prenosnik, namizni "
"računalnik ali strežnik)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:31
msgid ""
"Never make the Windows virtual IoT accessible from the public Internet. IoT "
"systems are designed to provide your database with access to devices on your "
"local network. Exposing them to the public Internet would create a "
"**security risk**."
msgstr ""
"Nikoli ne omogočite dostopa do virtualnega IoT sistema Windows z javnega "
"interneta. Sistemi IoT so zasnovani tako, da vaši zbirki podatkov zagotovijo "
"dostop do naprav v vašem lokalnem omrežju. Če jih izpostavite javnemu "
"internetu, bi ustvarili **varnostno tveganje**."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:38
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "Namestitev"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:40
msgid "To install the Windows virtual IoT on a Windows computer:"
msgstr "Za namestitev Windows virtual IoT na računalnik Windows:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:42
msgid ""
"Access `Odoo's download page <https://odoo.com/download>`_ and download the "
"**Community** edition of Odoo for Windows **matching your database's "
"version**."
msgstr ""
"Obiščite `stran za prenos Odoo <https://odoo.com/download>`_ in prenesite "
"izdajo **Community** Odoo za Windows, **ki ustreza različici vaše baze "
"podatkov**."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:44
msgid ""
"Open the downloaded :file:`.exe` file, allow the app to make changes to your "
"device, select a language, and click :guilabel:`OK`."
msgstr ""
"Odprite preneseno datoteko :file:`.exe`, dovolite aplikaciji, da naredi "
"spremembe na vaši napravi, izberite jezik in kliknite :guilabel:`OK`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:46
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Next`, then :guilabel:`I Agree` to accept the terms and "
"conditions and continue."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Next`, nato :guilabel:`I Agree`, da sprejmete pogoje in "
"nadaljujete."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:47
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Odoo IoT` from the :guilabel:`Select the type of install` "
"dropdown list. The following components should be selected: Odoo Server, "
"Odoo IoT, Nginx WebServer, and Ghostscript interpreter."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem seznamu :guilabel:`Izberite vrsto namestitve` izberite "
":guilabel:`Odoo IoT`. Izbrane morajo biti naslednje komponente: Odoo Server, "
"Odoo IoT, Nginx WebServer in Ghostscript interpreter."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:50
msgid ""
"Verify you have the required space on your computer and "
"click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Preverite, da imate na računalniku dovolj prostora, in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:51
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Destination folder`, enter C:\\\\odoo and "
"click :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr ""
"V :guilabel:`Destination folder` vnesite C:\\\\odoo in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Install`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:54
msgid ""
"Do not install Odoo's Windows virtual IoT in any Windows user directory, as "
"this can cause issues with :ref:`iot/https_certificate_iot/generation`."
msgstr ""
"Ne nameščajte Windows virtualnega IoT v nobeno uporabniško mapo sistema "
"Windows, saj lahko to povzroči težave z :ref:`iot/https_certificate_iot/"
"generation`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:57
msgid "Once the installation is complete, click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr "Ko je namestitev končana, kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:58
msgid ""
"Set up GPL Ghostscript: Click :guilabel:`Next`, agree to the terms and "
"conditions, click :guilabel:`Install`, then :guilabel:`Finish`."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite GPL Ghostscript: Kliknite :guilabel:`Next`, sprejmite pogoje, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Install`, nato :guilabel:`Finish`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:60
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Next`, :guilabel:`Next`, and :guilabel:`Finish` to complete "
"the setup. The :ref:`IoT system's homepage <iot/windows-iot/homepage>` "
"automatically opens in a web browser with the URL `http://localhost:8069`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`, :guilabel:`Naprej` in :guilabel:`Dokončaj`, da "
"dokončate nastavitev. :ref:`Domača stran sistema IoT <iot/windows-iot/"
"homepage>` se samodejno odpre v spletnem brskalniku z URL-jem `http://"
"localhost:8069`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:65
msgid ""
"If the web browser does not show anything, :ref:`restart <iot/windows_iot/"
"restart>` the Windows virtual IoT service."
msgstr ""
"Če spletni brskalnik ne prikaže ničesar, :ref:`ponovno zaženite <iot/"
"windows_iot/restart>` storitev Windows virtualnega IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:68
msgid ""
"Check that you can access the :ref:`IoT system's homepage <iot/windows-iot/"
"homepage>` in a web browser:"
msgstr ""
"Preverite, da lahko dostopate do :ref:`domače strani IoT sistema <iot/"
"windows-iot/homepage>` v spletnem brskalniku:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:71
msgid "on the Windows virtual IoT computer, and"
msgstr "na računalniku Windows virtual IoT in"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:72
msgid ""
"on another device **on the same network as the IoT system** by navigating to "
"the URL `http://xxx:8069` (where `xxx` is the IoT system's IP address)."
msgstr ""
"na drugi napravi **v istem omrežju kot IoT sistem** tako, da se pomaknete na "
"URL `http://xxx:8069` (kjer je `xxx` IP naslov IoT sistema)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:74
msgid ""
"on another device **on the same network as the IoT system** by navigating to "
"the URL `https://xxx` (where `xxx` is the IoT system's IP address) to test "
"for :doc:`HTTPS <iot_advanced/https_certificate_iot>` connection."
msgstr ""
"na drugi napravi **v istem omrežju kot sistem IoT** tako, da se pomaknete na "
"URL `https://xxx` (kjer je `xxx` IP naslov sistema IoT), da preizkusite "
":doc:`HTTPS <iot_advanced/https_certificate_iot>` povezavo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:79
msgid ""
"If you cannot access the :ref:`IoT system's homepage <iot/windows-iot/"
"homepage>` from another device, create a :ref:`Windows Firewall <iot/windows-"
"iot/firewall>` rule to allow communication through port `8069`."
msgstr ""
"Če ne morete dostopati do :ref:`domače strani IoT sistema <iot/windows-iot/"
"homepage>` z druge naprave, ustvarite pravilo :ref:`Windows Firewall <iot/"
"windows-iot/firewall>`, ki omogoča komunikacijo prek vrat `8069`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:86
msgid "Windows Firewall configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija Windows Firewall"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:88
msgid ""
"Firewalls help keep devices secure but can sometimes block legitimate "
"connections. If the Windows virtual IoT isn't accessible on the :abbr:`LAN "
"(Local Area Network)`, for example from another device, it could be due to a "
"firewall blocking the connection. To prevent this issue, configure "
"exceptions for network discovery in the :abbr:`OS (Operating System)` or "
"firewall settings."
msgstr ""
"Požarni zidovi pomagajo ohranjati naprave varne, vendar lahko včasih "
"blokirajo legitimne povezave. Če Windows virtualni IoT ni dosegljiv v "
":abbr:`LAN (krajevno omrežje)`, na primer z druge naprave, je lahko vzrok "
"požarni zid, ki blokira povezavo. Če želite preprečiti to težavo, "
"konfigurirajte izjeme za odkrivanje omrežja v nastavitvah :abbr:`OS "
"(operacijski sistem)` ali požarnega zidu."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:94
msgid ""
"If third-party firewall software is installed on the Windows computer, refer "
"to the software's documentation to configure firewall exceptions."
msgstr ""
"Če je na računalniku Windows nameščena programska oprema požarnega zidu "
"tretje osebe, glejte dokumentacijo programske opreme za konfiguracijo izjem "
"požarnega zidu."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:97
msgid ""
"To create a rule on Windows Defender and allow communication through port "
"`8069`, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti pravilo v Windows Defender in omogočiti komunikacijo "
"prek vrat `8069`, sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:100
msgid ""
"Search the Windows start menu for `firewall` and select "
"the :guilabel:`Windows Defender Firewall with Advanced Security` app."
msgstr ""
"V meniju za začetek sistema Windows poiščite `firewall` in izberite "
"aplikacijo :guilabel:`Windows Defender Firewall with Advanced Security`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:102
msgid "In the left part of the window, select :guilabel:`Inbound Rules`."
msgstr "V levem delu okna izberite :guilabel:`Inbound Rules`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:103
msgid ""
"In the right part of the window, under :guilabel:`Actions`, "
"click :guilabel:`New Rule`."
msgstr ""
"V desnem delu okna pod :guilabel:`Actions` kliknite :guilabel:`New Rule`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:104
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`New Inbound Rule Wizard` that opens, select "
"the :guilabel:`Port` type of rule and click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"V čarovniku :guilabel:`New Inbound Rule Wizard`, ki se odpre, izberite vrsto "
"pravila :guilabel:`Port` in kliknite :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:106
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Protocols and Ports` page, make sure :guilabel:`TCP` "
"and :guilabel:`Specified local ports` are selected, enter the following in "
"the field: `8069, 80, 443`, and click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Na strani :guilabel:`Protocols and Ports` se prepričajte, da sta "
"izbrana :guilabel:`TCP` in :guilabel:`Specified local ports`, v polje "
"vnesite naslednje: `8069, 80, 443` in kliknite :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:111
msgid ""
"Other ports may be necessary depending on your IoT devices. For example, for "
"the :doc:`/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/"
"worldline` payment terminal, add the `9050` port."
msgstr ""
"Drugi vrati so lahko potrebni glede na vaše IoT naprave. Na primer za "
"plačilni terminal :doc:`/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/"
"terminals/worldline` dodajte vrata `9050`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:115
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Action` page, select :guilabel:`Allow the connection` and "
"click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Na strani :guilabel:`Action` izberite :guilabel:`Allow the connection` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:117
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Profile` page, disable any connection type(s) that don't "
"apply to your Windows computer and click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Na strani :guilabel:`Profile` onemogočite vse vrste povezav, ki se ne "
"nanašajo na vaš računalnik Windows, in kliknite :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:119
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Name` page, provide a :guilabel:`Name` (e.g., `Odoo`) and, "
"optionally, a brief :guilabel:`Description`, then click :guilabel:`Finish`."
msgstr ""
"Na strani :guilabel:`Name` navedite :guilabel:`Name` (npr. `Odoo`) in po "
"želji kratek :guilabel:`Description`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Finish`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:123
msgid ""
"`Windows Firewall rules documentation <https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/"
"windows/security/operating-system-security/network-security/windows-firewall/"
"rules>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Windows Firewall rules documentation <https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/"
"windows/security/operating-system-security/network-security/windows-firewall/"
"rules>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:129
msgid "Windows virtual IoT homepage"
msgstr "Domača stran Windows virtual IoT"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:131
msgid ""
"To access the Windows virtual IoT's homepage, navigate to the URL `http://"
"localhost:8069` on the Windows virtual IoT computer or open a web browser "
"from another computer **on the same network as the IoT system** and navigate "
"to the URL `http://xxx:8069` (where `xxx` is the IoT system's IP address)."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do domače strani Windows virtual IoT se na računalniku Windows "
"virtual IoT pomaknite do URL-ja `http://localhost:8069` ali odprite spletni "
"brskalnik iz drugega računalnika **v istem omrežju kot sistem IoT** in se "
"pomaknite do URL-ja `http://xxx:8069` (kjer je `xxx` naslov IP sistema IoT)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:136
msgid ""
"Once the Windows virtual IoT is :doc:`connected to the Odoo database "
"<connect>`, its homepage can be accessed from Odoo by opening the IoT app "
"and clicking the URL displayed on the IoT system's card."
msgstr ""
"Ko je virtualni Windows IoT :doc:`povezan z bazo podatkov Odoo <connect>`, "
"je do njegove domače strani mogoče dostopati iz Odoo tako, da odprete "
"aplikacijo IoT in kliknete URL, prikazan na kartici sistema IoT."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:None
msgid "Windows virtual IoT's homepage"
msgstr "Domača stran Windows virtual IoT"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:145
msgid ""
"Make sure the :ref:`Windows Firewall is configured <iot/windows-iot/"
"firewall>` to allow access."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je :ref:`Windows Firewall is configured <iot/windows-iot/"
"firewall>` za dovoljenje dostopa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:148
msgid "Device connection"
msgstr "Povezava naprave"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:150
msgid ""
"Most :doc:`devices <devices>` automatically connect to the Windows computer "
"used for the Windows Virtual IoT through `Windows Plug and Play (PnP) "
"<https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/drivers/kernel/"
"introduction-to-plug-and-play>`_. However, if Windows does not recognize the "
"device automatically upon connection, the administrator may need to manually "
"install the appropriate drivers."
msgstr ""
"Večina :doc:`devices <devices>` se samodejno poveže z računalnikom Windows, "
"ki se uporablja za Windows Virtual IoT, prek `Windows Plug and Play (PnP) "
"<https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows-hardware/drivers/kernel/"
"introduction-to-plug-and-play>`_. Če pa Windows ne prepozna naprave "
"samodejno ob povezavi, bo administrator morda moral ročno namestiti ustrezne "
"gonilnike."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:157
msgid ""
"After connecting the devices to the computer, refresh the :ref:`IoT system's "
"homepage <iot/windows-iot/homepage>` to verify that the device is listed. If "
"the device does not appear, :ref:`reload the handlers <iot_updating_iot/"
"handlers>` from the :ref:`IoT system's homepage <iot/windows-iot/homepage>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko povežete naprave z računalnikom, osvežite :ref:`IoT system's homepage "
"<iot/windows-iot/homepage>`, da preverite, ali je naprava navedena. Če se "
"naprava ne prikaže, :ref:`reload the handlers <iot_updating_iot/handlers>` "
"z :ref:`IoT system's homepage <iot/windows-iot/homepage>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:165
msgid "Windows virtual IoT restart"
msgstr "Ponovni zagon Windows virtual IoT"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:167
msgid ""
"To manually restart the Windows IoT server, search the Windows start menu "
"for `services` and select the :guilabel:`Services` app. Scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`odoo-server-xxx` service (where `xxx` is the odoo version), "
"right-click it, and select :guilabel:`Start` or :guilabel:`Restart`."
msgstr ""
"Za ročni ponovni zagon strežnika Windows IoT poiščite v začetnem meniju "
"Windows `services` in izberite aplikacijo :guilabel:`Services`. Pomaknite se "
"navzdol do storitve :guilabel:`odoo-server-xxx` (kjer je `xxx` različica "
"Odoo), jo desno kliknite in izberite :guilabel:`Start` ali "
":guilabel:`Restart`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:174
msgid "Windows virtual IoT uninstall"
msgstr "Odstranitev Windows virtual IoT"

#: ../../content/applications/general/iot/windows_iot.rst:176
msgid ""
"To uninstall the Windows virtual IoT, `uninstall <https://"
"support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/uninstall-or-remove-apps-and-programs-in-"
"windows-4b55f974-2cc6-2d2b-d092-5905080eaf98#ID0EBD=Windows_11>`_ the Odoo "
"program on your Windows computer. Confirm the uninstallation and complete "
"the steps in the :guilabel:`Odoo Uninstall` dialog."
msgstr ""
"Za odstranitev Windows virtual IoT `uninstall <https://support.microsoft.com/"
"en-us/windows/uninstall-or-remove-apps-and-programs-in-"
"windows-4b55f974-2cc6-2d2b-d092-5905080eaf98#ID0EBD=Windows_11>`_ program "
"Odoo na računalniku Windows. Potrdite odstranitev in dokončajte korake v "
"pogovornem oknu :guilabel:`Odoo Uninstall`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo defines a *user* as someone who has access to a database. An "
"administrator can add as many users as the company needs and, in order to "
"restrict the type of information each user can access, rules can be applied "
"to each user. Users and access rights can be added and changed at any point."
msgstr ""
"Odoo definira *uporabnika* kot osebo, ki ima dostop do baze podatkov. "
"Skrbnik lahko doda toliko uporabnikov, kot jih podjetje potrebuje, in za "
"omejitev vrste informacij, do katerih ima vsak uporabnik dostop, lahko za "
"vsakega uporabnika določi pravila. Uporabnike in dostopne pravice je mogoče "
"dodajati in spreminjati kadarkoli."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:12
msgid ":doc:`users/language`"
msgstr ":doc:`users/language`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:13
msgid ":doc:`users/access_rights`"
msgstr ":doc:`users/access_rights`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`access-rights/superuser`"
msgstr ":ref:`access-rights/superuser`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:15
msgid ":ref:`access-rights/groups`"
msgstr ":ref:`access-rights/groups`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:20
msgid "Add individual users"
msgstr "Dodaj posamezne uporabnike"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:22
msgid ""
"To add new users, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users section "
"--> Manage Users`, and click on :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje novih uporabnikov pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"Nastavitve --> razdelek Uporabniki --> Upravljaj uporabnike` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Nov`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid "View of the settings page emphasizing the manage users field in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pogled strani nastavitev s poudarkom na polju za upravljanje uporabnikov v "
"Odooju."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:28
msgid ""
"Fill in the form with all the required information. Under the :doc:`Access "
"Rights <users/access_rights>` tab, choose the group within each application "
"the user can have access to."
msgstr ""
"Izpolnite obrazec z vsemi potrebnimi informacijami. V zavihku :doc:`Dostopne "
"pravice <users/access_rights>` izberite skupino v okviru vsake aplikacije, "
"do katere ima uporabnik lahko dostop."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:31
msgid ""
"The list of applications shown is based on the applications installed on the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Seznam prikazanih aplikacij temelji na aplikacijah, nameščenih v bazi "
"podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid "View of a user's form emphasizing the access rights tab in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pogled uporabniškega obrazca s poudarkom na zavihku dostopnih pravic v "
"Odooju."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:36
msgid ""
"After filling out all the necessary fields on the page, :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)`. An invitation email is automatically "
"sent to the user, using the email in the :guilabel:`Email Address` field. "
"The user must click on the link included in the email to accept the "
"invitation, and to create a database login."
msgstr ""
"Ko izpolnite vsa potrebna polja na strani, :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Shrani ročno)`. Uporabniku se samodejno pošlje e-"
"sporočilo s povabilom na naslov iz polja :guilabel:`E-poštni naslov`. "
"Uporabnik mora klikniti povezavo v e-sporočilu, da sprejme povabilo in "
"ustvari prijavo v bazo podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a user's form with a notification that the invitation email has been "
"sent in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pogled uporabniškega obrazca z obvestilom, da je bilo e-sporočilo s "
"povabilom poslano v Odooju."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:45
msgid ""
"If the company is on a monthly subscription plan, the database automatically "
"updates to reflect the added users. If the company is on a yearly or multi-"
"year plan, an expiration banner appears in the database. An upsell quotation "
"can be created by clicking the banner to update the subscription. "
"Alternatively, `send a support ticket <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ to "
"resolve the issue."
msgstr ""
"Če ima podjetje mesečni naročniški paket, se baza podatkov samodejno "
"posodobi, da odraža dodane uporabnike. Če ima podjetje letni ali večletni "
"paket, se v bazi podatkov prikaže pasica z opozorilom o poteku. Z klikom na "
"pasico je mogoče ustvariti ponudbo za nadgradnjo in posodobiti naročnino. "
"Druga možnost je `poslati zahtevek za podporo <https://www.odoo.com/help>`_ "
"za rešitev težave."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:52
msgid "User type"
msgstr "Vrsta uporabnika"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`User Type` can be chosen on the :guilabel:`Manage Users` page by "
"clicking on the search bar, and then :ref:`setting a filter <search/"
"preconfigured-filters>` for either :guilabel:`Internal User` "
"or :guilabel:`Portal User`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsto uporabnika` lahko izberete na strani :guilabel:`Upravljaj "
"uporabnike` s klikom na iskalno vrstico in nato :ref:`nastavitvijo filtra "
"<search/preconfigured-filters>` za :guilabel:`Notranji uporabnik` "
"ali :guilabel:`Uporabnik portala`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:58
msgid ""
"Odoo databases have three types of users: :guilabel:`Internal "
"User`, :guilabel:`Portal`, and :guilabel:`Public`. Users are considered "
"*internal database* users. Portal users are *external users*, who only have "
"access to the database portal to view records. Public users are those "
"visiting websites, via the website's frontend. See the documentation "
"on :doc:`users/portal`."
msgstr ""
"Baze podatkov Odoo imajo tri vrste uporabnikov: :guilabel:`Internal User`, "
":guilabel:`Portal` in :guilabel:`Public`. Uporabniki so *notranji uporabniki "
"baze podatkov*. Uporabniki portala so *zunanji uporabniki*, ki imajo dostop "
"le do portala baze podatkov za ogled zapisov. Javni uporabniki so tisti, ki "
"obiskujejo spletna mesta prek uporabniškega vmesnika spletnega mesta. Glejte "
"dokumentacijo na :doc:`users/portal`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:63
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Portal` user option does **not** allow the administrator to "
"choose access rights. These users have specific access rights pre-set (such "
"as, record rules and restricted menus), and usually do not belong to the "
"usual Odoo groups."
msgstr ""
"Možnost uporabnika :guilabel:`Portal` **ne** dovoli skrbniku izbire "
"dostopnih pravic. Ti uporabniki imajo vnaprej nastavljene določene dostopne "
"pravice (kot so pravila za zapise in omejeni meniji) in običajno ne sodijo v "
"običajne skupine Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:68
msgid "User devices"
msgstr "Naprave uporabnika"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:70
msgid ""
"For security purposes, when a user logs into the database, the various login "
"information, such as the IP address, is stored in the user's profile. It is "
"best practice to check this periodically, to ensure all access is from the "
"user, and no one else has accessed the database."
msgstr ""
"Iz varnostnih razlogov se ob prijavi uporabnika v zbirko podatkov različni "
"prijavni podatki, kot je naslov IP, shranijo v profil uporabnika. "
"Priporočljivo je to občasno preveriti, da se prepričate, da je ves dostop od "
"uporabnika in da nihče drug ni dostopal do zbirke podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:74
msgid ""
"To check the logged-in devices, click the user icon in the upper-right "
"corner, and click :guilabel:`My Profile`. This opens the user's profile in "
"the **Settings** app. Click the :guilabel:`Devices` tab to view a Kanban "
"list of all devices the user has logged into the database with. Any device "
"currently logged into the system displays a green circle next to the device "
"name on the Kanban card."
msgstr ""
"Za preverjanje prijavljenih naprav kliknite ikono uporabnika v zgornjem "
"desnem kotu in kliknite :guilabel:`Moj profil`. To odpre profil uporabnika v "
"aplikaciji **Nastavitve**. Kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Naprave`, da si "
"ogledate seznam Kanban vseh naprav, s katerimi se je uporabnik prijavil v "
"zbirko podatkov. Vsaka naprava, ki je trenutno prijavljena v sistem, prikaže "
"zelen krog poleg imena naprave na kartici Kanban."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid "The Kanban view of all user devices."
msgstr "Pogled Kanban vseh uporabnikovih naprav."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:83
msgid ""
"Click on a card to view the details for the device. Each card displays "
"the :guilabel:`User` name, the :guilabel:`Name` of the device, "
"the :guilabel:`Last IP Address` used as well as the :guilabel:`Linked IP "
"Address`. It also shows the :guilabel:`First Activity` and :guilabel:`Last "
"Activity`, which shows when the device first logged into the database, and "
"the last time it was active on the database."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na kartico, da si ogledate podrobnosti o napravi. Vsaka kartica "
"prikazuje ime :guilabel:`Uporabnika`, :guilabel:`Ime` "
"naprave, :guilabel:`Zadnji naslov IP`, ki je bil uporabljen, "
"ter :guilabel:`Povezan naslov IP`. Prikazuje tudi :guilabel:`Prvo aktivnost` "
"in :guilabel:`Zadnjo aktivnost`, kar prikazuje, kdaj se je naprava prvič "
"prijavila v zbirko podatkov in kdaj je bila nazadnje aktivna v zbirki "
"podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:89
msgid ""
"If a device is legitimate and should be retained, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Če je naprava legitimna in jo je treba obdržati, kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:91
msgid ""
"If the device is legitimate but should **not** be retained, and does not "
"pose a security risk, click :guilabel:`Delete`."
msgstr ""
"Če je naprava legitimna, vendar je **ne** bi smeli obdržati in ne "
"predstavlja varnostnega tveganja, kliknite :guilabel:`Izbriši`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid "The device details for one device."
msgstr "Podrobnosti naprave za eno napravo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:98
msgid "Revoke devices"
msgstr "Prekliči naprave"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:100
msgid ""
"If a listed device is **not** a legitimate user device, and could be a "
"potential security risk, remove the device and revoke access by clicking "
"the :guilabel:`Revoke` button."
msgstr ""
"Če navedena naprava **ni** legitimna uporabniška naprava in bi lahko "
"predstavljala varnostno tveganje, odstranite napravo in prekličite dostop s "
"klikom na gumb :guilabel:`Prekliči`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:103
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Security Control` pop-up window loads, asking to `Please "
"confirm your identity by entering your password`. Enter the user's password, "
"then click :guilabel:`Confirm Password`."
msgstr ""
"Odpre se pojavno okno :guilabel:`Varnostni nadzor`, ki zahteva `Please "
"confirm your identity by entering your password`. Vnesite uporabniško geslo "
"in kliknite :guilabel:`Confirm Password`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:106
msgid ""
"The device disappears from the :guilabel:`Devices` tab and can no longer be "
"used to log into the database."
msgstr ""
"Naprava izgine iz zavihka :guilabel:`Devices` in je ni več mogoče uporabiti "
"za prijavo v bazo podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:0
msgid ""
"The security pop-up window asking to verify the account with a password."
msgstr "Varnostno pojavno okno, ki zahteva preverjanje računa z geslom."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:115
msgid "Deactivate users"
msgstr "Deaktiviraj uporabnike"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:117
msgid ""
"To deactivate (i.e. archive) a user, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings "
"app --> Users section --> Manage Users`. Then, tick the checkbox to the left "
"of the users to be deactivated."
msgstr ""
"Za deaktiviranje (tj. arhiviranje) uporabnika pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Nastavitve --> razdelek Uporabniki --> "
"Upravljaj uporabnike`. Nato odkljukajte potrditveno polje levo od "
"uporabnikov, ki jih želite deaktivirati."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:120
msgid ""
"After selecting the appropriate user to be archived, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon, and select :guilabel:`Archive` from the "
"resulting drop-down menu. Then, click :guilabel:`OK` from "
"the :guilabel:`Confirmation` pop-up window that appears."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete ustreznega uporabnika za arhiviranje, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Dejanja)` in izberite :guilabel:`Arhiviraj` iz spustnega "
"menija, ki se prikaže. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`V redu` v pojavnem "
"oknu :guilabel:`Potrditev`, ki se prikaže."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:125
msgid ""
"**Never** deactivate the main/administrator user (admin). Making changes to "
"admin users can have a detrimental impact on the database. This includes "
"*impotent admin*, which means that no user in the database can make changes "
"to the access rights. For this reason, Odoo recommends contacting an Odoo "
"Business Analyst, or our Support Team, before making changes."
msgstr ""
"**Nikoli** ne deaktivirajte glavnega/administratorskega uporabnika (admin). "
"Spremembe na administratorskih uporabnikih lahko škodljivo vplivajo na bazo "
"podatkov. To vključuje *nezmožnega administratorja*, kar pomeni, da noben "
"uporabnik v bazi podatkov ne more spreminjati pravic dostopa. Iz tega "
"razloga Odoo priporoča, da se pred spremembami obrnete na poslovnega "
"analitika Odoo ali našo podporo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:131
msgid "Error: too many users"
msgstr "Napaka: preveč uporabnikov"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:133
msgid ""
"If there are more users in an Odoo database than provisioned in the Odoo "
"Enterprise subscription, the following message is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Če je v bazi podatkov Odoo več uporabnikov, kot je določeno v naročnini Odoo "
"Enterprise, se prikaže naslednje sporočilo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid "Too many users on a database error message."
msgstr "Sporočilo o napaki zaradi preveč uporabnikov v bazi podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:139
msgid ""
"When the message appears, the database administrator has 30 days to act "
"before the database expires. The countdown is updated every day."
msgstr ""
"Ko se sporočilo prikaže, ima administrator baze podatkov 30 dni za "
"ukrepanje, preden baza podatkov poteče. Odštevanje se posodablja vsak dan."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:142
msgid "To resolve the issue, either:"
msgstr "Za rešitev težave bodisi:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:144
msgid ""
"Add more users to the subscription by clicking the :guilabel:`Upgrade your "
"subscription` link displayed in the message to validate the upsell "
"quotation, and pay for the extra users."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte več uporabnikov v naročnino s klikom na povezavo :guilabel:`Nadgradi "
"svojo naročnino`, prikazano v sporočilu, da potrdite ponudbo za nadgradnjo "
"in plačate dodatne uporabnike."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:146
msgid ""
":ref:`Deactivate users <users/deactivate>`, and reject the upsell quotation."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Deaktivirajte uporabnike <users/deactivate>` in zavrnite ponudbo za "
"nadgradnjo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:149
msgid ""
"If the company is on a monthly subscription plan, the database automatically "
"updates to reflect the added users. If the company is on a yearly or multi-"
"year plan, an expiration banner appears in the database. An upsell quotation "
"can be created by clicking the banner to update the subscription. "
"Alternatively, users can `send a support ticket <https://www.odoo.com/"
"help>`_ to resolve the issue."
msgstr ""
"Če ima podjetje mesečno naročniško obdobje, se baza podatkov samodejno "
"posodobi in odraža dodane uporabnike. Če ima podjetje letno ali večletno "
"obdobje, se v bazi podatkov prikaže obvestilo o poteku. Ponudbo za "
"nadgradnjo lahko ustvarite s klikom na obvestilo za posodobitev naročnine. "
"Uporabniki lahko tudi `pošljejo zahtevek za podporo <https://www.odoo.com/"
"help>`_, da rešijo težavo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:155
msgid ""
"Once the database has the correct number of users, the expiration message "
"disappears automatically after a few days, when the next verification occurs."
msgstr ""
"Ko ima baza podatkov pravilno število uporabnikov, sporočilo o poteku "
"samodejno izgine po nekaj dneh, ko pride do naslednjega preverjanja."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:161
msgid "Password management"
msgstr "Upravljanje gesel"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:163
msgid ""
"Password management is an important part of granting users autonomous access "
"to the database at all times. Odoo offers a few different methods to reset a "
"user's password."
msgstr ""
"Upravljanje gesel je pomemben del zagotavljanja uporabnikom avtonomnega "
"dostopa do baze podatkov ves čas. Odoo ponuja nekaj različnih metod za "
"ponastavitev uporabniškega gesla."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:167
msgid ""
"Odoo has a setting to specify the length needed for a password. This setting "
"can be accessed by navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> "
"Permissions` section, and entering the desired password length in "
"the :guilabel:`Minimum Password Length` field. By default the value is `8`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ima nastavitev za določitev dolžine gesla. Do te nastavitve lahko "
"dostopate tako, da se pomaknete na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Nastavitve --> "
"razdelek Dovoljenja` in vnesete želeno dolžino gesla v polje "
":guilabel:`Minimalna dolžina gesla`. Privzeta vrednost je `8`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid ""
"Minimum Password Length highlighted in the Permissions section of General "
"Settings."
msgstr ""
"Minimalna dolžina gesla, označena v razdelku Dovoljenja v splošnih "
"nastavitvah."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:177
msgid "Reset password"
msgstr "Ponastavi geslo"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:179
msgid ""
"Sometimes, users might wish to reset their personal password for added "
"security, so they are the only ones with access to the password. Odoo offers "
"two different reset options: one initiated by the user to reset the "
"password, and another where the administrator triggers a reset."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki lahko včasih želijo ponastaviti svoje osebno geslo zaradi dodatne "
"varnosti, tako da so edini z dostopom do gesla. Odoo ponuja dve različni "
"možnosti ponastavitve: eno, ki jo sproži uporabnik za ponastavitev gesla, in "
"drugo, kjer administrator sproži ponastavitev."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:186
msgid "Enable password reset from login page"
msgstr "Omogoči ponastavitev gesla s prijavne strani"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:188
msgid ""
"It is possible to enable/disable password resets directly from the login "
"page. This action is completed by the individual user, and this setting is "
"enabled by default."
msgstr ""
"Mogoče je omogočiti/onemogočiti ponastavitev gesla neposredno s prijavne "
"strani. To dejanje izvede posamezen uporabnik, ta nastavitev pa je privzeto "
"omogočena."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:191
msgid ""
"To change this setting, go to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Permissions` "
"section, activate :guilabel:`Password Reset`, and then "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za spremembo te nastavitve pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> "
"razdelek Dovoljenja`, aktivirajte :guilabel:`Ponastavitev gesla` in nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid "Enabling Password Reset in Odoo Settings."
msgstr "Omogočanje ponastavitve gesla v nastavitvah Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:197
msgid ""
"On the login page, click :guilabel:`Reset Password` to initiate the password "
"reset process, and have a reset-token sent to the email on file."
msgstr ""
"Na prijavni strani kliknite :guilabel:`Ponastavi geslo`, da začnete postopek "
"ponastavitve gesla in prejmete žeton za ponastavitev na e-poštni naslov v "
"evidenci."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:203
msgid "Send reset instructions"
msgstr "Pošlji navodila za ponastavitev"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:205
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users & Companies --> Users`, select "
"the user from the list, and click on :guilabel:`Send Password Reset "
"Instructions` on the user form. An email is automatically sent to them with "
"password reset instructions."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Uporabniki in podjetja --> "
"Uporabniki`, izberite uporabnika s seznama in kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji "
"navodila za ponastavitev gesla` na obrazcu uporabnika. Uporabniku se "
"samodejno pošlje e-poštno sporočilo z navodili za ponastavitev gesla."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:210
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Send Password Reset Instructions` button **only** appears if "
"the Odoo invitation email has already been confirmed by the user. Otherwise, "
"a :guilabel:`Re-send Invitation Email` button appears."
msgstr ""
"Gumb :guilabel:`Pošlji navodila za ponastavitev gesla` se prikaže **samo**, "
"če je uporabnik že potrdil e-poštno vabilo Odoo. V nasprotnem primeru se "
"prikaže gumb :guilabel:`Ponovno pošlji e-poštno vabilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:214
msgid ""
"This email contains all the instructions needed to reset the password, along "
"with a link redirecting the user to an Odoo login page."
msgstr ""
"To e-poštno sporočilo vsebuje vsa potrebna navodila za ponastavitev gesla "
"skupaj s povezavo, ki uporabnika preusmeri na prijavno stran Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid "Example of an email with a password reset link for an Odoo account."
msgstr ""
"Primer e-poštnega sporočila s povezavo za ponastavitev gesla za račun Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:223
msgid "Change user password"
msgstr "Sprememba uporabniškega gesla"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:225
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users & Companies --> Users`, and "
"select a user to access its form. Click on the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon, and select :guilabel:`Change Password` from "
"the resulting drop-down menu. Enter a new password in the :guilabel:`New "
"Password` column of the :guilabel:`Change Password` pop-up window that "
"appears, and confirm the change by clicking :guilabel:`Change Password`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Uporabniki in podjetja --> "
"Uporabniki` in izberite uporabnika, da odprete njegov obrazec. Kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` in iz spustnega menija "
"izberite :guilabel:`Spremeni geslo`. V polje :guilabel:`Novo geslo` v "
"pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Spremeni geslo` vnesite novo geslo in potrdite "
"spremembo s klikom na :guilabel:`Spremeni geslo`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid "Change a user's password on Odoo."
msgstr "Sprememba uporabniškega gesla v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:235
msgid ""
"This operation only modifies the password of the users locally, and does "
"**not** affect their Odoo account."
msgstr ""
"Ta operacija spremeni geslo uporabnikov samo lokalno in **ne** vpliva na "
"njihov račun Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:238
msgid ""
"If the Odoo password needs to be changed, use the :ref:`send the password "
"reset <users/reset-password-email>`. Odoo.com passwords grant access to the "
"*My Databases* page, and other portal features."
msgstr ""
"Če je treba spremeniti geslo Odoo, :ref:`pošljite ponastavitev gesla <users/"
"reset-password-email>`. Gesla Odoo.com omogočajo dostop do strani *Moje "
"zbirke podatkov* in drugih portalnih funkcij."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:242
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Change Password`, the page is redirected to an "
"Odoo login page where the database can be re-accessed using the new password."
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na :guilabel:`Spremeni geslo` se stran preusmeri na prijavno stran "
"Odoo, kjer je mogoče ponovno dostopati do zbirke podatkov z novim geslom."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:248
msgid "Multi Companies"
msgstr "Več družb"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:250
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Multi Companies` field on a user form allows an administrator "
"to provide access to multiple companies for users. To configure a multi-"
"company environment for a user, navigate to the desired user by going "
"to: :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users section --> Manage users`. Then, "
"select the user to open their user form, and configure with multi-company "
"access."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Več podjetij` na obrazcu uporabnika omogoča skrbniku, da "
"uporabnikom zagotovi dostop do več podjetij. Za konfiguracijo večpodjetniške "
"okolja za uporabnika pojdite na želenega "
"uporabnika: :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Uporabniki --> Upravljanje "
"uporabnikov`. Nato izberite uporabnika, da odprete njegov obrazec, in ga "
"konfigurirajte z dostopom do več podjetij."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:255
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Multi Companies` in the :guilabel:`Access Rights` tab, set "
"the fields labeled :guilabel:`Allowed Companies` and :guilabel:`Default "
"Company`."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Več podjetij` na zavihku :guilabel:`Pravice dostopa` "
"nastavite polji z oznakama :guilabel:`Dovoljena podjetja` "
"in :guilabel:`Privzeto podjetje`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:258
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Allowed Companies` field can contain multiple companies. "
"These are the companies the user can access and edit, according to the set "
"access rights. The :guilabel:`Default Company` is the company the user "
"defaults to, upon logging in each time. This field can contain only **one** "
"company."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Dovoljena podjetja` lahko vsebuje več podjetij. To so "
"podjetja, do katerih ima uporabnik dostop in jih lahko ureja v skladu z "
"nastavljenimi pravicami dostopa. :guilabel:`Privzeto podjetje` je podjetje, "
"ki se uporabniku privzeto prikaže ob vsaki prijavi. To polje lahko vsebuje "
"samo **eno** podjetje."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:264
msgid ""
"If multi-company access is not configured correctly, it could lead to "
"inconsistent multi-company behaviors. Because of this, only experienced Odoo "
"users should make access rights changes to users for databases with a multi-"
"company configuration. For technical explanations, refer to the developer "
"documentation on :doc:`../../../developer/howtos/company`."
msgstr ""
"Če dostop do več podjetij ni pravilno konfiguriran, lahko to privede do "
"nedoslednega večpodjetniška vedenja. Zaradi tega naj spremembe pravic "
"dostopa za uporabnike v zbirkah podatkov z večpodjetniško konfiguracijo "
"izvajajo samo izkušeni uporabniki Odoo. Za tehnična pojasnila glejte "
"razvijalsko dokumentacijo na :doc:`../../../developer/howtos/company`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:None
msgid "View of a user's form emphasizing the multi companies field in Odoo."
msgstr "Pogled na obrazec uporabnika s poudarkom na polju več podjetij v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users.rst:273
msgid ":doc:`companies`"
msgstr ":doc:`companies`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:3
msgid "Two-factor authentication"
msgstr "Dvostopenjska avtentikacija"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:8
msgid ""
"*Two-factor authentication (2FA)* is a way to improve security, and prevent "
"unauthorized persons from accessing user accounts."
msgstr ""
"*Dvofaktorska avtentikacija (2FA)* je način za izboljšanje varnosti in "
"preprečevanje nepooblaščenim osebam dostop do uporabniških računov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:11
msgid ""
"Practically, |2fa| means storing a secret inside an *authenticator*, usually "
"on a mobile phone, and exchanging a code from the authenticator when trying "
"to log in."
msgstr ""
"Praktično |2fa| pomeni shranjevanje skrivnosti v *avtentikator*, običajno v "
"mobilnem telefonu, in izmenjavo kode iz avtentikatorja pri poskusu prijave."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:14
msgid ""
"This means an unauthorized user would need to guess the account password "
"*and* have access to the authenticator, which is a more difficult "
"proposition."
msgstr ""
"To pomeni, da bi moral nepooblaščen uporabnik uganiti geslo računa *in* "
"imeti dostop do avtentikatorja, kar je težja naloga."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:18
msgid ""
"Some governments, such as the :doc:`Australian <../../finance/"
"fiscal_localizations/australia>` government, require |2fa|. For "
"these :doc:`fiscal localizations <../../finance/fiscal_localizations>`, it "
"is not possible to deactivate |2fa|."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere vlade, kot je :doc:`avstralska <../../finance/fiscal_localizations/"
"australia>` vlada, zahtevajo |2fa|. Za te :doc:`davčne lokalizacije <../../"
"finance/fiscal_localizations>` ni mogoče deaktivirati |2fa|."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:23
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Zahteve"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:26
msgid ""
"These lists are just examples. They are **not** endorsements of any specific "
"software."
msgstr ""
"Ti seznami so samo primeri. **Niso** priporočila za določeno programsko "
"opremo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:28
msgid ""
"Phone-based authenticators are the easiest and most commonly used. Examples "
"include:"
msgstr ""
"Overjanje prek telefona je najlažje in najpogosteje uporabljeno. Primeri "
"vključujejo:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:30
msgid "`Authy <https://authy.com/>`_"
msgstr "`Authy <https://authy.com/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:31
msgid "`FreeOTP <https://freeotp.github.io/>`_"
msgstr "`FreeOTP <https://freeotp.github.io/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:32
msgid ""
"`Google Authenticator <https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/1066447?"
"hl=en>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Google Authenticator <https://support.google.com/accounts/answer/1066447?"
"hl=en>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:33
msgid "`LastPass Authenticator <https://lastpass.com/auth/>`_"
msgstr "`LastPass Authenticator <https://lastpass.com/auth/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:34
msgid ""
"`Microsoft Authenticator <https://www.microsoft.com/en-gb/account/"
"authenticator?cmp=h66ftb_42hbak>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Microsoft Authenticator <https://www.microsoft.com/en-gb/account/"
"authenticator?cmp=h66ftb_42hbak>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:37
msgid "Password managers are another option. Common examples include:"
msgstr "Upravitelji gesel so druga možnost. Pogosti primeri vključujejo:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:39
msgid "`1Password <https://support.1password.com/one-time-passwords/>`_"
msgstr "`1Password <https://support.1password.com/one-time-passwords/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:40
msgid "`Bitwarden <https://bitwarden.com/help/article/authenticator-keys/>`_"
msgstr "`Bitwarden <https://bitwarden.com/help/article/authenticator-keys/>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:43
msgid ""
"The remainder of this document uses Google Authenticator as an example, as "
"it is one of the most commonly used. This is **not** an endorsement of the "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Preostanek tega dokumenta uporablja Google Authenticator kot primer, saj je "
"eden najpogosteje uporabljenih. To **ni** priporočilo izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:49
msgid "Two-factor authentication setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev dvofaktorske avtentikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:51
msgid ""
"After selecting an authenticator, log in to Odoo, then click the profile "
"avatar in the upper-right corner, and select :guilabel:`My Profile` from the "
"resulting drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Po izbiri avtentikatorja se prijavite v Odoo, nato kliknite avatar profila v "
"zgornjem desnem kotu in v spustnem meniju izberite :guilabel:`Moj profil`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:54
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Account Security` tab, then slide the :guilabel:`Two-"
"Factor Authentication` toggle to *active*."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Varnost računa`, nato premaknite "
"stikalo :guilabel:`Dvofaktorska avtentikacija` na *aktivno*."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:60
msgid ""
"This generates a :guilabel:`Security Control` pop-up window that requires "
"password confirmation to continue. Enter the appropriate password, then "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm Password`. Next, a :guilabel:`Two-Factor "
"Authentication Activation` pop-up window appears, with a |QR|."
msgstr ""
"To ustvari pojavno okno :guilabel:`Varnostni nadzor`, ki za nadaljevanje "
"zahteva potrditev gesla. Vnesite ustrezno geslo, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi geslo`. Nato se prikaže pojavno "
"okno :guilabel:`Aktivacija dvofaktorske avtentikacije` z |QR|."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:68
msgid ""
"Using the desired authenticator application, scan the |QR| when prompted."
msgstr "Z izbrano aplikacijo za avtentikacijo skenirajte |QR|, ko ste pozvani."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:71
msgid ""
"If scanning the screen is not possible (e.g. the setup is being completed on "
"the *same* device as the authenticator application), clicking the "
"provided :guilabel:`Cannot scan it?` link, or copying the secret to manually "
"set up the authenticator, is an alternative."
msgstr ""
"Če skeniranje zaslona ni mogoče (npr. nastavitev se izvaja na *isti* napravi "
"kot aplikacija avtentikatorja), je alternativa klik na podano povezavo "
":guilabel:`Ne morete skenirati?` ali kopiranje skrivnosti za ročno "
"nastavitev avtentikatorja."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:81
msgid "Afterwards, the authenticator should display a *verification code*."
msgstr "Nato naj bi avtentikator prikazal *potrditveno kodo*."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:86
msgid ""
"Enter the code into the :guilabel:`Verification Code` field, then "
"click :guilabel:`Activate`."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite kodo v polje :guilabel:`Potrditvena koda`, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Aktiviraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:92
msgid "Logging in"
msgstr "Prijava"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:94
msgid "To confirm |2fa| setup is complete, log out of Odoo."
msgstr "Za potrditev, da je nastavitev |2fa| končana, se odjavite iz Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:96
msgid ""
"On the login page, input the username and password, then "
"click :guilabel:`Log in`. On the :guilabel:`Two-factor Authentication` page, "
"input the code provided by the chosen authenticator in "
"the :guilabel:`Authentication Code` field, then click :guilabel:`Log in`."
msgstr ""
"Na prijavni strani vnesite uporabniško ime in geslo, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Prijava`. Na strani :guilabel:`Dvofaktorska "
"avtentikacija` vnesite kodo, ki jo zagotovi izbrani avtentikator, v "
"polje :guilabel:`Avtentikacijska koda`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Prijava`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:None
msgid "The login page with 2fa enabled."
msgstr "Prijavna stran z omogočeno dvofaktorsko avtentikacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:105
msgid ""
"If a user loses access to their authenticator, an administrator **must** "
"deactivate |2fa| on the account before the user can log in."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabnik izgubi dostop do svojega avtentikatorja, **mora** skrbnik "
"deaktivirati |2fa| na računu, preden se lahko uporabnik prijavi."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:109
msgid "Enforce two-factor authentication"
msgstr "Uveljavi dvofaktorsko preverjanje pristnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:111
msgid ""
"To enforce the use of |2fa| for all users, first navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Main Odoo Dashboard --> Apps`. Remove "
"the :guilabel:`Apps` filter from the :guilabel:`Search...` bar, then search "
"for `2FA by mail`."
msgstr ""
"Za uveljavitev uporabe |2fa| za vse uporabnike najprej pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Glavna nadzorna plošča Odoo --> Aplikacije`. Odstranite "
"filter :guilabel:`Aplikacije` iz vrstice :guilabel:`Iskanje...`, nato "
"poiščite `2FA by mail`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:115
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Install` on the Kanban card for the :guilabel:`2FA by mail` "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Namesti` na kartici Kanban za modul :guilabel:`2FA by "
"mail`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:None
msgid "The 2FA by mail module in the Apps directory."
msgstr "Modul 2FA by mail v imeniku aplikacij."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:121
msgid ""
"After installation is complete, go to :guilabel:`Settings app: Permissions`. "
"Tick the checkbox labeled, :guilabel:`Enforce two-factor authentication`. "
"Then, use the radio buttons to choose whether to apply this setting "
"to :guilabel:`Employees only`, or :guilabel:`All users`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je namestitev končana, pojdite na :guilabel:`Aplikacija Nastavitve: "
"Dovoljenja`. Označite potrditveno polje z oznako :guilabel:`Uveljavi "
"dvofaktorsko avtentikacijo`. Nato uporabite radijske gumbe, da izberete, ali "
"želite to nastavitev uporabiti za :guilabel:`Samo zaposlene` ali "
":guilabel:`Vse uporabnike`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:126
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`All users` applies the setting to portal users, in "
"addition to employees."
msgstr ""
"Izbira :guilabel:`Vsi uporabniki` uporabi nastavitev za uporabnike portala, "
"poleg zaposlenih."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:None
msgid "The enforce two factor setting in the Settings application."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev uveljavljanja dvofaktorske avtentikacije v aplikaciji Nastavitve."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/2fa.rst:132
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save` to commit any unsaved changes."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`, da potrdite vse neshranjene spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:3
msgid "Access rights"
msgstr "Pravice dostopa"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Access rights* are permissions that determine the content and applications "
"users can access and edit. In Odoo, these permissions can be set for "
"individual users or for groups of users. Limiting permissions to only those "
"who need them ensures that users do not modify or delete anything they "
"should not have access to."
msgstr ""
"*Pravice dostopa* so dovoljenja, ki določajo vsebino in aplikacije, do "
"katerih lahko uporabniki dostopajo in jih urejajo. V Odoo je ta dovoljenja "
"mogoče nastaviti za posamezne uporabnike ali za skupine uporabnikov. "
"Omejitev dovoljenj samo na tiste, ki jih potrebujejo, zagotavlja, da "
"uporabniki ne spremenijo ali izbrišejo ničesar, do česar ne bi smeli imeti "
"dostopa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:10
msgid "**Only** an *administrator* can change access rights."
msgstr "**Samo** *administrator* lahko spremeni pravice dostopa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:13
msgid ""
"Making changes to access rights can have a detrimental impact on the "
"database. This includes *impotent admin*, which means that no user in the "
"database can make changes to the access rights. For this reason, Odoo "
"recommends contacting an Odoo Business Analyst, or our Support Team, before "
"making changes."
msgstr ""
"Spremembe pravic dostopa lahko škodljivo vplivajo na bazo podatkov. To "
"vključuje *nesposobnega administratorja*, kar pomeni, da noben uporabnik v "
"bazi podatkov ne more spreminjati pravic dostopa. Zato Odoo priporoča, da se "
"pred izvajanjem sprememb obrnete na poslovnega analitika Odoo ali našo ekipo "
"za podporo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:19
msgid ""
"A user **must** have the specific *Administration* access rights set on "
"their user profile, in order to make changes on another user's settings for "
"access rights."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik **mora** imeti v svojem uporabniškem profilu nastavljene določene "
"pravice dostopa za *administracijo*, da lahko spreminja nastavitve pravic "
"dostopa drugega uporabnika."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:22
msgid ""
"To access this setting, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Manage "
"users --> select a user --> Access Rights tab --> Administration section --> "
"Administration field`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do te nastavitve pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> "
"Upravljanje uporabnikov --> izberite uporabnika --> zavihek Pravice dostopa "
"--> razdelek Administracija --> polje Administracija`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:25
msgid ""
"Once at the setting, an already existing administrator **must** change the "
"setting in the :guilabel:`Administration` field to :guilabel:`Access Rights`."
msgstr ""
"Na tej nastavitvi **mora** obstoječi administrator spremeniti nastavitev v "
"polju :guilabel:`Administracija` na :guilabel:`Pravice dostopa`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:28
msgid ""
"Once complete, click :guilabel:`Save` to save the changes, and implement the "
"user as an administrator."
msgstr ""
"Ko je postopek končan, kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`, da shranite spremembe in "
"uvedete uporabnika kot administratorja."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:36
msgid ""
"The access rights for :ref:`individual users <users/add-individual>` are set "
"when the user is added to the database, but they can be adjusted at any "
"point in the user's profile."
msgstr ""
"Pravice dostopa za :ref:`posamezne uporabnike <users/add-individual>` se "
"nastavijo, ko je uporabnik dodan v bazo podatkov, vendar jih je mogoče kadar "
"koli prilagoditi v uporabniškem profilu."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:39
msgid ""
"To make changes to a user's rights, click on the desired user to edit their "
"profile."
msgstr ""
"Za spremembe pravic uporabnika kliknite na želenega uporabnika in uredite "
"njegov profil."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:None
msgid ""
"Users menu in the Users & Companies section of the Settings app of Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Meni Uporabniki v razdelku Uporabniki in podjetja v aplikaciji Nastavitve "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:44
msgid ""
"On the user's profile page, in the :guilabel:`Access Rights` tab, scroll "
"down to view the current permissions."
msgstr ""
"Na profilni strani uporabnika v zavihku :guilabel:`Pravice dostopa` se "
"pomaknite navzdol, da si ogledate trenutna dovoljenja."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:47
msgid ""
"For each app, use the drop-down menu to select what level of permission this "
"user should have. The options vary for each section, yet the most common "
"are: :guilabel:`Blank/None`, :guilabel:`User: Own "
"Documents`, :guilabel:`User: All Documents`, or :guilabel:`Administrator`."
msgstr ""
"Za vsako aplikacijo uporabite spustni meni, da izberete, katero raven "
"dovoljenja naj ima ta uporabnik. Možnosti se razlikujejo za vsak razdelek, "
"najpogostejše pa so: :guilabel:`Prazno/Brez`, :guilabel:`Uporabnik: lastni "
"dokumenti`, :guilabel:`Uporabnik: vsi dokumenti` "
"ali :guilabel:`Administrator`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:51
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Administration` field in the :guilabel:`Access Rights` tab "
"has the following options: :guilabel:`Settings` or :guilabel:`Access Rights`."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Administracija` v zavihku :guilabel:`Pravice dostopa` ima "
"naslednje možnosti: :guilabel:`Nastavitve` ali :guilabel:`Pravice dostopa`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:None
msgid "The Sales apps drop-down menu to set the user's level of permissions."
msgstr ""
"Spustni meni aplikacij Prodaja za nastavitev uporabnikove ravni dovoljenj."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:60
msgid "Create and modify groups"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje in spreminjanje skupin"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:62
msgid ""
"*Groups* are app-specific sets of permissions that are used to manage common "
"access rights for a large amount of users. Administrators can modify the "
"existing groups in Odoo, or create new ones to define rules for models "
"within an application."
msgstr ""
"*Skupine* so aplikacijsko-specifični nabori dovoljenj, ki se uporabljajo za "
"upravljanje skupnih dostopnih pravic za veliko število uporabnikov. "
"Administratorji lahko spremenijo obstoječe skupine v Odoo ali ustvarijo nove "
"za določanje pravil za modele znotraj aplikacije."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:66
msgid ""
"To access groups, first activate Odoo's :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, then go to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users & Companies --> "
"Groups`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do skupin najprej aktivirajte Odoo :ref:`razvijalski način "
"<developer-mode>`, nato pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Nastavitve --> "
"Uporabniki in podjetja --> Skupine`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:None
msgid ""
"Groups menu in the Users & Companies section of the Settings app of Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Meni Skupine v razdelku Uporabniki in podjetja v aplikaciji Nastavitve v "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:72
msgid ""
"To create a new group from the :guilabel:`Groups` page, "
"click :guilabel:`Create`. Then, from the blank group form, select "
"an :guilabel:`Application`, and complete the group form (detailed below)."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nove skupine na strani :guilabel:`Skupine` "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari`. Nato iz praznega obrazca skupine "
"izberite :guilabel:`Aplikacijo` in izpolnite obrazec skupine (podrobno "
"spodaj)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:75
msgid ""
"To modify existing groups, click on an existing group from the list "
"displayed on the :guilabel:`Groups` page, and edit the contents of the form."
msgstr ""
"Za spreminjanje obstoječih skupin kliknite na obstoječo skupino s seznama, "
"prikazanega na strani :guilabel:`Skupine`, in uredite vsebino obrazca."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:78
msgid ""
"Enter a :guilabel:`Name` for the group and tick the checkbox next "
"to :guilabel:`Share Group`, if this group was created to set access rights "
"for sharing data with some users."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite :guilabel:`Ime` za skupino in označite potrditveno polje "
"poleg :guilabel:`Skupina za skupno rabo`, če je bila ta skupina ustvarjena "
"za nastavitev dostopnih pravic za deljenje podatkov z nekaterimi uporabniki."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:82
msgid ""
"Always test the settings being changed to ensure they are being applied to "
"the correct users."
msgstr ""
"Vedno preizkusite nastavitve, ki jih spreminjate, da zagotovite, da se "
"uporabljajo za pravilne uporabnike."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:84
msgid ""
"The group form contains multiple tabs for managing all elements of the "
"group. In each tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add a new row for users "
"or rules, and click the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(cancel)` icon to remove "
"a row."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec skupine vsebuje več zavihkov za upravljanje vseh elementov skupine. "
"V vsakem zavihku kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da dodate novo vrstico "
"za uporabnike ali pravila, in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(prekliči)`, da odstranite vrstico."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:None
msgid "Tabs in the Groups form to modify the settings of the group."
msgstr "Zavihki v obrazcu Skupine za spreminjanje nastavitev skupine."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Users` tab: lists the current users in the group. Users listed in "
"black have administrative rights. Users without administrative access appear "
"in blue. Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add users to this group."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Uporabniki`: navaja trenutne uporabnike v skupini. "
"Uporabniki, navedeni v črni barvi, imajo administratorske pravice. "
"Uporabniki brez administratorskega dostopa so prikazani v modri barvi. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da dodate uporabnike v to skupino."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:94
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Inherited` tab: Inherited means that users added to this group "
"are automatically added to the groups listed on this tab. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add inherited groups."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Podedovano`: Podedovano pomeni, da so uporabniki, dodani "
"tej skupini, samodejno dodani skupinam, navedenim v tem zavihku. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da dodate podedovane skupine."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:98
msgid ""
"For example, if the group *Sales/Administrator* lists the group *Website/"
"Restricted Editor* in its :guilabel:`Inherited` tab, then any users added to "
"the *Sales/Administrator* group automatically receive access to the *Website/"
"Restricted Editor* group, as well."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če skupina *Prodaja/Administrator* v svojem "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Podedovano` navaja skupino *Spletna stran/Omejeni "
"urednik*, potem vsi uporabniki, dodani skupini *Prodaja/Administrator*, "
"samodejno prejmejo dostop tudi do skupine *Spletna stran/Omejeni urednik*."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Menus` tab: defines which models the group can have access to. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add a specific menu."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Meniji`: določa, do katerih modelov lahko ima skupina "
"dostop. Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da dodate določen meni."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Views` tab: lists which views in Odoo the group has access to. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add a view to the group."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Pogledi`: navaja, do katerih pogledov v Odoo ima skupina "
"dostop. Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da skupini dodate pogled."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Access Rights` tab: lists the first level of rights (models) that "
"this group has. The :guilabel:`Name` column represents the name for the "
"current group's access to the model selected in the :guilabel:`Model` column."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Pravice dostopa`: prikazuje prvo raven pravic (modele), "
"ki jih ima ta skupina. Stolpec :guilabel:`Ime` predstavlja ime dostopa "
"trenutne skupine do modela, izbranega v stolpcu :guilabel:`Model`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:110
msgid ""
"To link a new access right to a group, click :guilabel:`Add a line`. Select "
"the appropriate model from the :guilabel:`Model` drop-down, then enter a "
"name for the access right in the :guilabel:`Name` column. For each model, "
"enable the following options as appropriate:"
msgstr ""
"Za povezavo nove pravice dostopa s skupino kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"vrstico`. Iz spustnega seznama :guilabel:`Model` izberite ustrezen model, "
"nato vnesite ime pravice dostopa v stolpec :guilabel:`Ime`. Za vsak model po "
"potrebi omogočite naslednje možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:114
msgid ":guilabel:`Read`: Users can see the object's existing values."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Branje`: Uporabniki lahko vidijo obstoječe vrednosti objekta."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:115
msgid ":guilabel:`Write`: Users can edit the object's existing values."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pisanje`: Uporabniki lahko urejajo obstoječe vrednosti objekta."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:116
msgid ":guilabel:`Create`: Users can create new values for the object."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ustvarjanje`: Uporabniki lahko ustvarjajo nove vrednosti za "
"objekt."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:117
msgid ":guilabel:`Delete`: Users can delete values for the object."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Brisanje`: Uporabniki lahko brišejo vrednosti objekta."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:120
msgid ""
"While there are no conventions for naming access rights, it is advisable to "
"choose a name that identifies its purpose."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav ne obstajajo konvencije za poimenovanje pravic dostopa, je "
"priporočljivo izbrati ime, ki identificira njegov namen."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:123
msgid ""
"For example, the access that purchase managers have to "
"the :guilabel:`Contact` model could be named `res.partner.purchase.manager`. "
"This consists of the technical name of the model, followed by a name "
"identifying the group of users in question."
msgstr ""
"Naprimer, dostop, ki ga imajo vodje nabave do modela :guilabel:`Stik`, bi se "
"lahko imenoval `res.partner.purchase.manager`. To je sestavljeno iz "
"tehničnega imena modela, ki mu sledi ime, ki identificira zadevno skupino "
"uporabnikov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:0
msgid "Name of access rights to a model."
msgstr "Ime pravic dostopa do modela."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:130
msgid ""
"To find the model's technical name from the current view, first enter a "
"placeholder text in the :guilabel:`Name` field, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Model` name, then the :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(Internal link)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Za iskanje tehničnega imena modela iz trenutnega pogleda najprej vnesite "
"nadomestno besedilo v polje :guilabel:`Ime`, nato kliknite "
"ime :guilabel:`Model`, nato ikono :icon:`fa-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`(Notranja povezava)`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:134
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Record Rules`: lists the second layer of editing and visibility "
"rights. :guilabel:`Record Rules` overwrite, or refine, the group's access "
"rights. Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add a record rule to this group. For "
"each rule, choose values for the following options:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pravila zapisov`: prikazuje drugo plast pravic urejanja in "
"vidnosti. :guilabel:`Pravila zapisov` prepišejo ali izboljšajo pravice "
"dostopa skupine. Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da dodate pravilo "
"zapisa tej skupini. Za vsako pravilo izberite vrednosti za naslednje "
"možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:138
msgid ":guilabel:`Apply for Read`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uporabi za branje`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:139
msgid ":guilabel:`Apply for Write`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uporabi za pisanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:140
msgid ":guilabel:`Apply for Create`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uporabi za ustvarjanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:141
msgid ":guilabel:`Apply for Delete`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uporabi za brisanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:144
msgid ""
"Record rules are written using a *domain*, or conditions that filter data. A "
"domain expression is a list of such conditions. For example:"
msgstr ""
"Pravila zapisov so napisana z uporabo *domene* ali pogojev, ki filtrirajo "
"podatke. Izraz domene je seznam takih pogojev. Na primer:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:147
msgid ""
"`[('mrp_production_ids', 'in', "
"user.partner_id.commercial_partner_id.production_ids.ids)]`"
msgstr ""
"`[('mrp_production_ids', 'in', "
"user.partner_id.commercial_partner_id.production_ids.ids)]`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:149
msgid ""
"This record rule is to enable MRP consumption warnings for subcontractors."
msgstr "To pravilo zapisa omogoča opozorila o porabi MRP za podizvajence."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:151
msgid ""
"Odoo has a library of preconfigured record rules for ease of use. Users "
"without knowledge of domains (and domain expressions) should consult an Odoo "
"Business Analyst, or the Odoo Support Team, before making changes."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ima knjižnico vnaprej konfiguriranih pravil zapisov za enostavno "
"uporabo. Uporabniki brez znanja o domenah (in izrazih domen) se morajo pred "
"izvajanjem sprememb posvetovati z Odoo poslovnim analitikom ali ekipo za "
"podporo Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:158
msgid "Superuser mode"
msgstr "Način nadzornega uporabnika"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:160
msgid ""
"*Superuser mode* allows the user to bypass record rules and access rights. "
"To activate *Superuser mode*, first, activate :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>`. Then, navigate to the *debug* menu, represented by "
"a :icon:`fa-bug` :guilabel:`(debug)` icon, located in the top banner."
msgstr ""
"*Nadprivilegirani način* uporabniku omogoča, da se izogne pravilom zapisov "
"in pravicam dostopa. Če želite aktivirati *nadprivilegirani način*, najprej "
"aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>`. Nato se pomaknite do "
"menija *razhroščevanje*, ki ga predstavlja ikona :icon:`fa-"
"bug` :guilabel:`(razhroščevanje)`, ki se nahaja v zgornjem pasicu."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:164
msgid ""
"Finally, towards the bottom of the menu, click :guilabel:`Become Superuser`."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu, proti dnu menija, kliknite :guilabel:`Postani nadprivilegiran`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:167
msgid ""
"Only users with *Settings* access for the *Administration* section of the "
"*Access Rights* (in their user profile) are allowed to log in to *Superuser "
"mode*."
msgstr ""
"Le uporabniki z dostopom *Nastavitve* za razdelek *Administracija* v "
"*Pravicah dostopa* (v svojem uporabniškem profilu) se lahko prijavijo v "
"*nadprivilegirani način*."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:171
msgid ""
"*Superuser mode* allows for circumvention of record rules and access rights, "
"and therefore, should be exercised with extreme caution."
msgstr ""
"*Nadprivilegirani način* omogoča izogibanje pravilom zapisov in pravicam "
"dostopa, zato ga je treba izvajati z izjemno previdnostjo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:174
msgid ""
"Upon exiting *Superuser mode*, users may be locked out of the database, due "
"to changes that were made. This can cause *impotent admin*, or an "
"administrator without the ability to change access rights/settings."
msgstr ""
"Po izhodu iz *nadprivilegiranega načina* so lahko uporabniki izključeni iz "
"zbirke podatkov zaradi sprememb, ki so bile narejene. To lahko povzroči "
"*onemogočenega skrbnika* ali skrbnika brez možnosti spreminjanja pravic "
"dostopa/nastavitev."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:178
msgid ""
"In this case contact Odoo Support here: `new help ticket <https://"
"www.odoo.com/help>`_. The support team is able to restore access using a "
"support login."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru se obrnite na podporo Odoo tukaj: `nov zahtevek za pomoč "
"<https://www.odoo.com/help>`_. Ekipa za podporo lahko obnovi dostop z "
"uporabo prijave za podporo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:181
msgid ""
"To leave *Superuser mode*, log out of the account, by navigating to the "
"upper-right corner, and clicking on the :guilabel:`OdooBot` username. Then, "
"select the :guilabel:`Log out` option."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zapustiti *nadprivilegirani način*, se odjavite iz računa tako, da "
"se pomaknete v zgornji desni kot in kliknete na uporabniško "
"ime :guilabel:`OdooBot`. Nato izberite možnost :guilabel:`Odjava`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:185
msgid ""
"An alternative way to activate *Superuser mode* is to login as a superuser. "
"To do that, navigate to the login screen, and enter the "
"appropriate :guilabel:`Email` and :guilabel:`Password`."
msgstr ""
"Alternativen način za aktivacijo *načina superskrbnika* je prijava kot "
"superskrbnik. Za to se pomaknite na prijavni zaslon in vnesite ustrezni "
":guilabel:`E-pošta` in :guilabel:`Geslo`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/access_rights.rst:188
msgid ""
"Instead of clicking :guilabel:`Login`, click :guilabel:`Log in as superuser`."
msgstr ""
"Namesto da kliknete :guilabel:`Prijava`, kliknite :guilabel:`Prijavi se kot "
"nadprivilegiran`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:3
msgid "Microsoft Azure sign-in authentication"
msgstr "Preverjanje pristnosti prijave Microsoft Azure"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Microsoft Azure OAuth sign-in authentication is a useful function that "
"allows Odoo users to sign in to their database with their Microsoft Azure "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Preverjanje pristnosti prijave Microsoft Azure OAuth je uporabna funkcija, "
"ki uporabnikom Odoo omogoča, da se prijavijo v svojo zbirko podatkov s "
"svojim računom Microsoft Azure."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:8
msgid ""
"This is particularly helpful if the organization uses Azure Workspace, and "
"wants employees within the organization to connect to Odoo using their "
"Microsoft Accounts."
msgstr ""
"To je še posebej koristno, če organizacija uporablja Azure Workspace in "
"želi, da se zaposleni v organizaciji povežejo z Odoo z uporabo svojih "
"računov Microsoft."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:12
msgid ""
"Databases hosted on Odoo.com should not use OAuth login for the owner or "
"administrator of the database as it would unlink the database from their "
"Odoo.com account. If OAuth is set up for that user, the database will no "
"longer be able to be duplicated, renamed, or otherwise managed from the "
"Odoo.com portal."
msgstr ""
"Zbirke podatkov, gostovane na Odoo.com, ne smejo uporabljati prijave OAuth "
"za lastnika ali skrbnika zbirke podatkov, saj bi to prekinilo povezavo "
"zbirke podatkov z njihovim računom Odoo.com. Če je OAuth nastavljen za tega "
"uporabnika, zbirke podatkov ne bo več mogoče podvojiti, preimenovati ali "
"kako drugače upravljati s portala Odoo.com."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:18
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/calendar/outlook`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/calendar/outlook`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:19
msgid ":doc:`../email_communication/azure_oauth`"
msgstr ":doc:`../email_communication/azure_oauth`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:24
msgid ""
"Integrating the Microsoft sign-in function requires configuration on "
"Microsoft and Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Integracija funkcije prijave Microsoft zahteva konfiguracijo v Microsoftu in "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:27
msgid "Odoo System Parameter"
msgstr "Sistemski parameter Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:29
msgid ""
"First activate the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>`, and then go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters`."
msgstr ""
"Najprej aktivirajte :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-mode>`, nato pa "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Tehnično --> Sistemski parametri`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:32
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create` and on the new/blank form that appears, add the "
"following system parameter `auth_oauth.authorization_header` to "
"the :guilabel:`Key` field, and set the :guilabel:`Value` to `1`. Then "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to finish."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari` in v novem obrazcu, ki se pojavi, dodajte "
"naslednji sistemski parameter `auth_oauth.authorization_header` v polje "
":guilabel:`Ključ` ter nastavite :guilabel:`Vrednost` na `1`. Nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Shrani`, da končate."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:37
msgid "Microsoft Azure dashboard"
msgstr "Nadzorna plošča Microsoft Azure"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:42
msgid ""
"Now that the system parameters in Odoo have been set up, it's time to create "
"a corresponding application inside of Microsoft Azure. To get started "
"creating the new application, go to `Microsoft's Azure Portal <https://"
"portal.azure.com/>`_. Log in with the :guilabel:`Microsoft Outlook Office "
"365` account if there is one, otherwise, log in with a "
"personal :guilabel:`Microsoft account`."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj ko so sistemski parametri v Odoo nastavljeni, je čas, da ustvarite "
"ustrezno aplikacijo v Microsoft Azure. Če želite začeti ustvarjati novo "
"aplikacijo, pojdite na `Microsoftov portal Azure <https://portal.azure.com/"
">`_. Prijavite se z računom :guilabel:`Microsoft Outlook Office 365`, če ga "
"imate, sicer se prijavite z osebnim :guilabel:`računom Microsoft`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:49
msgid ""
"A user with administrative access to the *Azure Settings* must connect and "
"perform the following configuration steps below."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik z upraviteljskim dostopom do *nastavitev Azure* se mora povezati "
"in izvesti spodnje konfiguracijske korake."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:52
msgid ""
"Next, navigate to the section labeled :guilabel:`Manage Microsoft Entra ID` "
"(formally *Azure Active Directory*). The location of this link is usually in "
"the center of the page."
msgstr ""
"Nato se pomaknite do razdelka z oznako :guilabel:`Manage Microsoft Entra ID` "
"(prej *Azure Active Directory*). Ta povezava se običajno nahaja na sredini "
"strani."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:55
msgid ""
"Now, click on the :guilabel:`Add (+)` icon, located in the top menu, and "
"then select :guilabel:`App registration` from the drop-down menu. On "
"the :guilabel:`Register an application` screen, rename the :guilabel:`Name` "
"field to `Odoo Login OAuth` or a similarly recognizable title. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Supported account types` section select the option "
"for :guilabel:`Accounts in this organizational directory only (Default "
"Directory only - Single tenant)`."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj kliknite na ikono :guilabel:`Add (+)`, ki se nahaja v zgornjem meniju, "
"in nato izberite :guilabel:`App registration` iz spustnega menija. Na "
"zaslonu :guilabel:`Register an application` preimenujte "
"polje :guilabel:`Name` v `Odoo Login OAuth` ali podobno prepoznavno ime. Pod "
"razdelkom :guilabel:`Supported account types` izberite "
"možnost :guilabel:`Accounts in this organizational directory only (Default "
"Directory only - Single tenant)`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:62
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Supported account types` can vary by Microsoft account type "
"and end use of the OAuth. For example: Is the login meant for internal users "
"within one organization or is it meant for customer portal access? The above "
"configuration is used for internal users in an organization."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Supported account types` se lahko razlikujejo glede na vrsto "
"Microsoftovega računa in končno uporabo OAuth. Na primer: Ali je prijava "
"namenjena notranjim uporabnikom znotraj ene organizacije ali je namenjena "
"dostopu do portala za stranke? Zgornja konfiguracija se uporablja za "
"notranje uporabnike v organizaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:67
msgid ""
"Choose :guilabel:`Personal Microsoft accounts only` if the target audience "
"is meant for portal users. Choose :guilabel:`Accounts in this organizational "
"directory only (Default Directory only - Single tenant)` if the target "
"audience is company users."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Personal Microsoft accounts only`, če je ciljna skupina "
"namenjena uporabnikom portala. Izberite :guilabel:`Accounts in this "
"organizational directory only (Default Directory only - Single tenant)`, če "
"je ciljna skupina uporabniki podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:71
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Redirect URL` section, select :guilabel:`Web` as the "
"platform, and then input `https://<odoo base url>/auth_oauth/signin` in "
"the :guilabel:`URL` field. The Odoo base :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource "
"Locator)` is the canonical domain at which your Odoo instance can be reached "
"(e.g. *mydatabase.odoo.com* if you are hosted on Odoo.com) in "
"the :guilabel:`URL` field. Then, click :guilabel:`Register`, and the "
"application is created."
msgstr ""
"Pod razdelkom :guilabel:`Redirect URL` izberite :guilabel:`Web` kot "
"platformo in nato vnesite `https://<odoo base url>/auth_oauth/signin` v "
"polje :guilabel:`URL`. Osnovna :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` Odoo "
"je kanonična domena, prek katere je mogoče dostopati do vaše instance Odoo "
"(npr. *mydatabase.odoo.com*, če gostujete na Odoo.com) v "
"polju :guilabel:`URL`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Register` in aplikacija je "
"ustvarjena."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:78
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Avtentikacija"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:80
msgid ""
"Edit the new app's authentication by clicking on "
"the :guilabel:`Authentication` menu item in the left menu after being "
"redirected to the application's settings from the previous step."
msgstr ""
"Uredite preverjanje pristnosti nove aplikacije tako, da po preusmerjanju na "
"nastavitve aplikacije iz prejšnjega koraka kliknete na element "
"menija :guilabel:`Authentication` v levem meniju."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:83
msgid ""
"Next, the type of *tokens* needed for the OAuth authentication will be "
"chosen. These are not currency tokens but rather authentication tokens that "
"are passed between Microsoft and Odoo. Therefore, there is no cost for these "
"tokens; they are used merely for authentication purposes between "
"two :abbr:`APIs (application programming interfaces)`. Select the tokens "
"that should be issued by the authorization endpoint by scrolling down the "
"screen and check the boxes labeled: :guilabel:`Access tokens (used for "
"implicit flows)` and :guilabel:`ID tokens (used for implicit and hybrid "
"flows)`."
msgstr ""
"Nato bosta izbrani vrsti *žetonov*, potrebnih za preverjanje pristnosti "
"OAuth. To niso valutni žetoni, temveč preveritveni žetoni, ki se izmenjujejo "
"med Microsoftom in Odoo. Zato ti žetoni niso plačljivi; uporabljajo se le za "
"preverjanje pristnosti med dvema :abbr:`APIs (application programming "
"interfaces)`. Izberite žetone, ki naj jih izda avtorizacijska končna točka, "
"tako da se pomaknete navzdol po zaslonu in označite polja z "
"oznakami: :guilabel:`Access tokens (used for implicit flows)` "
"in :guilabel:`ID tokens (used for implicit and hybrid flows)`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:None
msgid "Authentication settings and endpoint tokens."
msgstr "Nastavitve preverjanja pristnosti in žetoni končnih točk."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:95
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save` to ensure these settings are saved."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Save`, da shranite te nastavitve."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:98
msgid "Gather credentials"
msgstr "Zbiranje poverilnic"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:100
msgid ""
"With the application created and authenticated in the Microsoft Azure "
"console, credentials will be gathered next. To do so, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Overview` menu item in the left-hand column. Select and copy "
"the :guilabel:`Application (client) ID` in the window that appears. Paste "
"this credential to a clipboard / notepad, as this credential will be used in "
"the Odoo configuration later."
msgstr ""
"Ko je aplikacija ustvarjena in overjena v konzoli Microsoft Azure, bodo nato "
"zbrane poverilnice. To storite tako, da kliknete na element "
"menija :guilabel:`Overview` v levem stolpcu. V prikazanem oknu izberite in "
"kopirajte :guilabel:`Application (client) ID`. Te poverilnice prilepite v "
"odložišče / beležko, saj bodo uporabljene pri kasnejši konfiguraciji Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:105
msgid ""
"After finishing this step, click on :guilabel:`Endpoints` on the top menu "
"and click the *copy icon* next to :guilabel:`OAuth 2.0 authorization "
"endpoint (v2)` field. Paste this value in the clipboard / notepad."
msgstr ""
"Po zaključku tega koraka kliknite :guilabel:`Endpoints` v zgornjem meniju in "
"kliknite *ikono za kopiranje* poleg polja :guilabel:`OAuth 2.0 authorization "
"endpoint (v2)`. To vrednost prilepite v odložišče / beležko."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:None
msgid "Application ID and OAuth 2.0 authorization endpoint (v2) credentials."
msgstr ""
"ID aplikacije in poverilnice končne točke za avtorizacijo OAuth 2.0 (v2)."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:114
#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:111
msgid "Odoo setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:116
msgid ""
"Finally, the last step in the Microsoft Azure OAuth configuration is to "
"configure some settings in Odoo. Navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> "
"Integrations --> OAuth Authentication` and check the box to activate the "
"OAuth login feature. Click :guilabel:`Save` to ensure the progress is saved. "
"Then, sign in to the database once the login screen loads."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje je zadnji korak pri konfiguraciji Microsoft Azure OAuth nastavitev "
"v Odoo. Pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Integracije --> "
"Preverjanje pristnosti OAuth` in potrdite polje za aktivacijo funkcije "
"prijave OAuth. Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`, da shranite napredek. Nato se "
"prijavite v bazo podatkov, ko se naloži prijavni zaslon."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:121
msgid ""
"Once again, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> Integrations --> OAuth "
"Authentication` and click on :guilabel:`OAuth Providers`. Now, "
"select :guilabel:`New` in the upper-left corner and name the provider "
"`Azure`."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno pojdite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Integracije --> "
"Preverjanje pristnosti OAuth` in kliknite na :guilabel:`Ponudniki OAuth`. "
"Zdaj izberite :guilabel:`Novo` v zgornjem levem kotu in poimenujte ponudnika "
"`Azure`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:125
msgid ""
"Paste the :guilabel:`Application (client) ID` from the previous section into "
"the :guilabel:`Client ID` field. After completing this, paste the "
"new :guilabel:`OAuth 2.0 authorization endpoint (v2)` value into "
"the :guilabel:`Authorization URL` field."
msgstr ""
"Prilepite :guilabel:`ID aplikacije (odjemalca)` iz prejšnjega razdelka v "
"polje :guilabel:`ID odjemalca`. Po tem prilepite novo vrednost "
":guilabel:`Končna točka za avtorizacijo OAuth 2.0 (v2)` v polje "
":guilabel:`URL za avtorizacijo`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:129
msgid ""
"For the :guilabel:`UserInfo URL` field, paste the following :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)`: `https://graph.microsoft.com/oidc/userinfo`"
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`UserInfo URL` prilepite naslednji :abbr:`URL (Uniform "
"Resource Locator)`: `https://graph.microsoft.com/oidc/userinfo`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:132
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Scope` field, paste the following value: `openid profile "
"email`. Next, the Windows logo can be used as the CSS class on the login "
"screen by entering the following value: `fa fa-fw fa-windows`, in "
"the :guilabel:`CSS class` field."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Scope` prilepite naslednjo vrednost: `openid profile "
"email`. Nato lahko kot razred CSS na prijavnem zaslonu uporabite logotip "
"Windows tako, da vnesete naslednjo vrednost: `fa fa-fw fa-windows` v "
"polje :guilabel:`CSS class`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:136
msgid ""
"Check the box next to the :guilabel:`Allowed` field to enable the OAuth "
"provider. Finally, add `Microsoft Azure` to the :guilabel:`Login button "
"label` field. This text will appear next to the Windows logo on the login "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Označite polje poleg :guilabel:`Allowed`, da omogočite ponudnika OAuth. "
"Nazadnje dodajte `Microsoft Azure` v polje :guilabel:`Login button label`. "
"To besedilo se bo prikazalo poleg logotipa Windows na prijavni strani."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:None
msgid "Odoo provider setup in the Settings application."
msgstr "Nastavitev ponudnika Odoo v aplikaciji Settings."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:144
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Save` the changes to complete the OAuth authentication setup in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Save` spremembe, da dokončate nastavitev preverjanja pristnosti "
"OAuth v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:147
msgid "User experience flows"
msgstr "Uporabniške izkušnje"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:149
msgid ""
"For a user to log in to Odoo using Microsoft Azure, the user must be on "
"the :menuselection:`Odoo password reset page`. This is the only way that "
"Odoo is able to link the Microsoft Azure account and allow the user to log "
"in."
msgstr ""
"Uporabnik se lahko v Odoo prijavi z Microsoftom Azure le, če je "
"na :menuselection:`strani za ponastavitev gesla Odoo`. To je edini način, s "
"katerim lahko Odoo poveže račun Microsoft Azure in uporabniku omogoči "
"prijavo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:154
msgid ""
"Existing users must :ref:`reset their password <users/reset-password>` to "
"access the :menuselection:`Odoo password reset page`. New Odoo users must "
"click the new user invitation link that was sent via email, then click "
"on :guilabel:`Microsoft Azure`. Users should not set a new password."
msgstr ""
"Obstoječi uporabniki morajo :ref:`ponastaviti geslo <users/reset-password>`, "
"da lahko dostopajo do :menuselection:`strani za ponastavitev gesla Odoo`. "
"Novi uporabniki Odoo morajo klikniti na povezavo za povabilo novega "
"uporabnika, ki je bila poslana po e-pošti, nato pa klikniti "
"na :guilabel:`Microsoft Azure`. Uporabniki naj ne nastavljajo novega gesla."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:159
msgid ""
"To sign in to Odoo for the first time using the Microsoft Azure OAuth "
"provider, navigate to the :menuselection:`Odoo password reset page` (using "
"the new user invitation link). A password reset page should appear. Then, "
"click on the option labeled :guilabel:`Microsoft Azure`. The page will "
"redirect to the Microsoft login page."
msgstr ""
"Za prvo prijavo v Odoo z Microsoftovim ponudnikom OAuth Azure se pomaknite "
"na :menuselection:`stran za ponastavitev gesla Odoo` (z uporabo povezave za "
"povabilo novega uporabnika). Prikazati se mora stran za ponastavitev gesla. "
"Nato kliknite na možnost z oznako :guilabel:`Microsoft Azure`. Stran vas bo "
"preusmerila na Microsoftovo prijavno stran."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:None
msgid "Microsoft Outlook login page."
msgstr "Prijavna stran Microsoft Outlook."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:168
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Microsoft Email Address` and click :guilabel:`Next`. "
"Follow the process to sign in to the account. Should :abbr:`2FA (Two Factor "
"Authentication)` be turned on, then an extra step may be required."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite :guilabel:`e-poštni naslov Microsoft` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`. Sledite postopku za prijavo v račun. Če je "
"vklopljena :abbr:`2FA (dvofaktorska avtentikacija)`, bo morda potreben "
"dodatni korak."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:None
msgid "Enter Microsoft login credentials."
msgstr "Vnesite prijavne podatke za Microsoft."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:176
msgid ""
"Finally, after logging in to the account, the page will redirect to a "
"permissions page where the user will be prompted to :guilabel:`Accept` the "
"conditions that the Odoo application will access their Microsoft information."
msgstr ""
"Končno se bo po prijavi v račun stran preusmerila na stran s pravicami, kjer "
"bo uporabnik pozvan, da :guilabel:`Sprejme` pogoje, da bo aplikacija Odoo "
"dostopala do njegovih Microsoftovih podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/azure.rst:None
msgid ""
"Accept Microsoft conditions for permission access to your account "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Sprejmite Microsoftove pogoje za dovoljenje dostopa do podatkov vašega "
"računa."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:3
msgid "Facebook sign-in authentication"
msgstr "Preverjanje pristnosti s prijavo prek Facebooka"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Facebook* OAuth sign-in function allows Odoo users to sign in to their "
"database with their Facebook account."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija *Facebook* OAuth za prijavo omogoča uporabnikom Odoo, da se "
"prijavijo v svojo podatkovno bazo s svojim Facebook računom."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:9
msgid ""
"Databases housed on Odoo.com should **not** use OAuth login for the owner or "
"administrator of the database, as it would unlink the database from their "
"Odoo.com account. If OAuth is setup for that user, the database can no "
"longer be duplicated, renamed, or otherwise managed from the Odoo.com portal."
msgstr ""
"Podatkovne baze, nameščene na Odoo.com, **ne smejo** uporabljati prijave "
"OAuth za lastnika ali skrbnika podatkovne baze, saj bi to odpravilo povezavo "
"podatkovne baze z njihovim računom Odoo.com. Če je OAuth nastavljen za tega "
"uporabnika, podatkovne baze ni več mogoče podvajati, preimenovati ali kako "
"drugače upravljati iz portala Odoo.com."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:15
msgid "Meta for Developers setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev Meta for Developers"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:17
msgid ""
"Go to `Meta for Developers <https://developers.facebook.com/>`_ and log in. "
"Click :guilabel:`My Apps`. On the :guilabel:`Apps` page, "
"click :guilabel:`Create App`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na `Meta for Developers <https://developers.facebook.com/>`_ in se "
"prijavite. Kliknite :guilabel:`Moje aplikacije`. Na "
"strani :guilabel:`Aplikacije` kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari aplikacijo`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:20
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Use cases` page, select :guilabel:`Authenticate and "
"request data from users with Facebook Login`, then click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Na strani :guilabel:`Primeri uporabe` izberite :guilabel:`Avtentikacija in "
"zahtevanje podatkov od uporabnikov s prijavo prek Facebooka`, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:23
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Add an app name` field, enter `Odoo Login OAuth`, or a "
"similar title."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Dodaj ime aplikacije` vnesite `Odoo Login OAuth` ali "
"podoben naslov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:26
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`App contact email` automatically defaults to the email "
"address associated with the Meta account. If this email address is not "
"regularly monitored, it may be wise to use another email address."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`E-poštni naslov za stik z aplikacijo` se samodejno nastavi "
"na e-poštni naslov, povezan z Meta računom. Če se ta e-poštni naslov ne "
"preverja redno, je morda pametno uporabiti drug e-poštni naslov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:30
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Next`. Review the :guilabel:`Publishing requirements`, "
"the :guilabel:`Meta Platform Terms`, and :guilabel:`Developer Policies`. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Create app`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Naprej`. Preglejte :guilabel:`Zahteve za "
"objavo`, :guilabel:`Pogoje Meta Platform` in :guilabel:`Pravilnike za "
"razvijalce`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari aplikacijo`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:34
msgid "Clicking :guilabel:`Create app` may require password re-entry."
msgstr ""
"Klik na :guilabel:`Ustvari aplikacijo` lahko zahteva ponoven vnos gesla."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:37
msgid "Customize app"
msgstr "Prilagajanje aplikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:39
msgid ""
"After the new app is created, the :guilabel:`Dashboard` page appears, with a "
"list of steps to be completed before the app can be published. From here, "
"click :guilabel:`Customize adding a Facebook Login button`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je nova aplikacija ustvarjena, se prikaže stran :guilabel:`Nadzorna "
"plošča` s seznamom korakov, ki jih je treba opraviti, preden je aplikacijo "
"mogoče objaviti. Tukaj kliknite :guilabel:`Prilagodi dodajanje gumba za "
"prijavo prek Facebooka`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:None
msgid "The App Dashboard in the Meta for developers platform."
msgstr "Nadzorna plošča aplikacije na platformi Meta for developers."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:47
msgid "On the :guilabel:`Customize` page, click :guilabel:`Settings`."
msgstr "Na strani :guilabel:`Prilagodi` kliknite :guilabel:`Nastavitve`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:49
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Valid OAuth Redirect URIs` field, enter `https://<odoo "
"base url>/auth_oauth/signin`, replacing `<odoo base url>` with the URL of "
"the applicable database."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Veljavni URI-ji za preusmeritev OAuth` vnesite `https://"
"<odoo base url>/auth_oauth/signin`, pri čemer zamenjajte `<odoo base url>` z "
"URL-jem ustrezne podatkovne baze."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:53
msgid ""
"If a database has the URL `https://example.odoo.com`, the URL `https://"
"example.odoo.com/auth_oauth/signin` would be entered in the :guilabel:`Valid "
"OAuth Redirect URIs` field."
msgstr ""
"Če ima podatkovna baza URL `https://example.odoo.com`, bi bil URL `https://"
"example.odoo.com/auth_oauth/signin` vnešen v polje :guilabel:`Valid OAuth "
"Redirect URIs`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:57
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Save changes` when finished."
msgstr "Ko končate, kliknite :guilabel:`Save changes`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:60
msgid "Configure settings"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje nastavitev"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:62
msgid ""
"At the far left of the page, click :menuselection:`App settings --> Basic`. "
"This page contains additional settings that are required before the app can "
"be submitted for approval."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani strani kliknite :menuselection:`App settings --> Basic`. Ta "
"stran vsebuje dodatne nastavitve, ki so potrebne, preden je mogoče "
"aplikacijo poslati v odobritev."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:65
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Privacy Policy URL` field, enter `https://www.odoo.com/"
"privacy`."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Privacy Policy URL` vnesite `https://www.odoo.com/"
"privacy`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:68
msgid ""
"`<https://www.odoo.com/privacy>`_ is the default privacy policy for "
"databases hosted on Odoo.com."
msgstr ""
"`<https://www.odoo.com/privacy>`_ je privzeta politika zasebnosti za "
"podatkovne baze, gostovane na Odoo.com."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:70
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`App Icon` field to open a file upload window. From "
"here, select and upload an app icon."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite polje :guilabel:`App Icon`, da odprete okno za nalaganje datotek. "
"Od tu izberite in naložite ikono aplikacije."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:73
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`User data deletion` field, enter `https://www.odoo.com/"
"documentation/17.0/administration/odoo_accounts.html`."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`User data deletion` vnesite `https://www.odoo.com/"
"documentation/17.0/administration/odoo_accounts.html`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:77
msgid ""
"This document provides instructions on how a user can delete their Odoo "
"account."
msgstr ""
"Ta dokument podaja navodila, kako lahko uporabnik izbriše svoj Odoo račun."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/facebook.rst:79
msgid ""
"Lastly, click the :guilabel:`Category` field, and select :guilabel:`Business "
"and pages` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje kliknite polje :guilabel:`Category` in iz spustnega menija "
