msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Set up your LDAP Server` list, click :guilabel:`New`, then "
"select the required company in the dropdown list."
msgstr ""
"Na seznamu :guilabel:`Nastavi strežnik LDAP` klikni :guilabel:`Novo`, nato "
