"v polji :guilabel:`Naslov strežnika LDAP` oziroma :guilabel:`Vrata strežnika "
"LDAP`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:15
msgid ""
"Enable :guilabel:`Use TLS` to request secure TLS/SSL encryption when "
"connecting to the LDAP server, providing the server has StartTLS enabled."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči :guilabel:`Uporabi TLS`, da zahteva varno šifriranje TLS/SSL pri "
"povezovanju s strežnikom LDAP, če ima strežnik omogočen StartTLS."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:17
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Login information` section, enter the ID and password of "
"the account used to query the server in the :guilabel:`LDAP binddn` "
"and :guilabel:`LDAP password` fields, respectively. If the fields are left "
"empty, the server will perform the query anonymously."
msgstr ""
"V odseku :guilabel:`Podatki za prijavo` vnesi ID in geslo računa, "
"uporabljenega za poizvedovanje strežnika, v polji :guilabel:`LDAP binddn` "
"oziroma :guilabel:`Geslo LDAP`. Če sta polji prazni, bo strežnik izvajal "
"poizvedbe anonimno."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:20
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Process parameter` section, enter:"
msgstr "V odseku :guilabel:`Parameter procesa` vnesi:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:22
msgid ""
"the LDAP server's name in the :guilabel:`LDAP base` field using LDAP format "
"(e.g., ``dc=example,dc=com``);"
msgstr ""
"ime strežnika LDAP v polje :guilabel:`Osnova LDAP` v obliki LDAP (npr. "
"``dc=example,dc=com``);"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:24
msgid "``uid=%s`` in the :guilabel:`LDAP filter` field."
msgstr "``uid=%s`` v polje :guilabel:`Filter LDAP`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:26
msgid "In the :guilabel:`User information` section:"
msgstr "V odseku :guilabel:`Podatki o uporabniku`:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:28
msgid ""
"Enable :guilabel:`Create user` to create a user profile in Odoo the first "
"time someone logs in using LDAP;"
msgstr ""
"Omogoči :guilabel:`Ustvari uporabnika`, da se ob prvi prijavi prek LDAP "
"ustvari uporabniški profil v Odoo;"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:30
msgid ""
"Select the :guilabel:`User template` to be used to create the new user "
"profiles. If no template is selected, the administrator's profile is used."
msgstr ""
"Izberi :guilabel:`Predlogo uporabnika`, ki bo uporabljena za ustvarjanje "
"novih uporabniških profilov. Če predloga ni izbrana, se uporabi "
"administratorjev profil."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:34
msgid ""
"When using Microsoft Active Directory (AD) for LDAP authentication, if users "
"experience login issues despite using valid credentials, create a new system "
"parameter to disable referral chasing in the LDAP client:"
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi Microsoft Active Directory (AD) za preverjanje pristnosti LDAP, "
"če uporabniki naletijo na težave pri prijavi kljub veljavnim poverilom, "
"ustvari nov sistemski parameter za onemogočanje sledenja napotitev v "
"odjemalcu LDAP:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:38
msgid ":ref:`Activate the developer mode. <developer-mode>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Aktiviraj razvijalski način. <developer-mode>`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:39
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters` and "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdi na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Tehnično --> Sistemski parametri` in "
"klikni :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:41
msgid "Fill in the fields:"
msgstr "Izpolni polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:43
msgid ":guilabel:`Key`: ``auth_ldap.disable_chase_ref``"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ključ`: ``auth_ldap.disable_chase_ref``"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/ldap.rst:44
msgid ":guilabel:`Value`: ``True``"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vrednost`: ``True``"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:3
msgid "Portal access"
msgstr "Dostop do portala"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:7
msgid ""
"Portal access is given to users who need the ability to view certain "
"documents or information within an Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Dostop do portala je dodeljen uporabnikom, ki potrebujejo možnost ogled "
"določenih dokumentov ali informacij v bazi podatkov Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:10
msgid ""
"Some common use cases for providing portal access include allowing customers "
"to read/view any or all of the following in Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Nekateri pogosti primeri uporabe za zagotavljanje dostopa do portala "
"vključujejo omogočanje strankam, da berejo/pregledujejo katerekoli ali vse "
"naslednje v Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:13
msgid "leads/opportunities"
msgstr "potencialne stranke/priložnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:14
msgid "quotations/sales orders"
msgstr "ponudbe/prodajne naloge"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:15
msgid "purchase orders"
msgstr "nabavne naloge"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:16
msgid "invoices & bills"
msgstr "fakture in računi"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:17
msgid "projects"
msgstr "projekti"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:18
msgid "tasks"
msgstr "naloge"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:19
msgid "timesheets"
msgstr "časovnice"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:20
msgid "tickets"
msgstr "zahtevki"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:21
msgid "signatures"
msgstr "podpisi"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:22
msgid "subscriptions"
msgstr "naročnine"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:25
msgid ""
"Portal users only have read/view access, and will not be able to edit any "
"documents in the database."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki portala imajo samo dostop za branje/ogled in ne bodo mogli "
"urejati nobenih dokumentov v bazi podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:31
msgid "Provide portal access to customers"
msgstr "Zagotovite strankam dostop do portala"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:33
msgid ""
"From the main Odoo dashboard, select the :guilabel:`Contacts` application. "
"If the contact is not yet created in the database, click on "
"the :guilabel:`Create` button, enter the details of the contact, and then "
"click :guilabel:`Save`. Otherwise, choose an existing contact, and then "
"click on the :guilabel:`Action` drop-down menu located at the top-center of "
"the interface."
msgstr ""
"Z glavne Odoo nadzorne plošče izberite aplikacijo :guilabel:`Stiki`. Če stik "
"v zbirki podatkov še ni ustvarjen, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Ustvari`, "
"vnesite podrobnosti stika in nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`. V nasprotnem "
"primeru izberite obstoječi stik in nato kliknite spustni meni "
":guilabel:`Dejanje`, ki se nahaja na vrhu vmesnika na sredini."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:None
msgid "Use the Contacts application to give portal access to users."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite aplikacijo Stiki, da uporabnikom omogočite dostop do portala."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:42
msgid ""
"Then select :guilabel:`Grant portal access`. A pop-up window appears, "
"listing three fields:"
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite :guilabel:`Dodeli dostop do portala`. Prikaže se pojavno okno "
"s tremi polji:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:44
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contact`: the recorded name of the contact in the Odoo database"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Stik`: zapisano ime stika v zbirki podatkov Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:45
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Email`: the contact's email address that they will use to log "
"into the portal"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`E-pošta`: e-poštni naslov stika, ki ga bo uporabil za prijavo v "
"portal"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`In Portal`: whether or not the user has portal access"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Na portalu`: ali ima uporabnik dostop do portala ali ne"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:48
msgid ""
"To grant portal access, first enter the contact's :guilabel:`Email` they "
"will use to log into the portal. Then, check the box under the :guilabel:`In "
"Portal` column. Optionally, add text to the invitation message the contact "
"will receive. Then click :guilabel:`Apply` to finish."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodeliti dostop do portala, najprej vnesite :guilabel:`E-pošto` "
"stika, ki jo bo uporabil za prijavo v portal. Nato označite polje v stolpcu "
":guilabel:`Na portalu`. Po želji dodajte besedilo k vabilnemu sporočilu, ki "
"ga bo stik prejel. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi`, da končate."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:None
msgid ""
"An email address and corresponding checkbox for the contact need to be "
"filled in before\n"
"sending a portal invitation."
msgstr ""
"E-poštni naslov in ustrezno potrditveno polje za stik morata biti izpolnjena "
"pred\n"
"pošiljanjem vabila na portal."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:57
msgid ""
"An email will be sent to the specified email address, indicating that the "
"contact is now a portal user for that Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Na navedeni e-poštni naslov bo poslano e-poštno sporočilo z obvestilom, da "
"je stik zdaj uporabnik portala za to zbirko podatkov Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:61
msgid ""
"To grant portal access to multiple users at once, navigate to a company "
"contact, then click :menuselection:`Action --> Grant portal access` to view "
"a list of all of the company's related contacts. Check the box under "
"the :guilabel:`In Portal` column for all the contacts that need portal "
"access, then click :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite hkrati dodeliti dostop do portala več uporabnikom, pojdite na stik "
"podjetja in nato kliknite :menuselection:`Dejanje --> Dodeli dostop do "
"portala`, da si ogledate seznam vseh povezanih stikov podjetja. Označite "
"polje v stolpcu :guilabel:`Na portalu` za vse stike, ki potrebujejo dostop "
"do portala, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:67
msgid ""
"At any time, portal access can be revoked by navigating to the contact, "
"clicking :menuselection:`Action --> Grant portal access`, and then "
"unselecting the checkbox under the :guilabel:`In Portal` column and "
"clicking :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr ""
"Dostop do portala je mogoče kadarkoli preklicati tako, da pojdete na stik, "
"kliknete :menuselection:`Dejanje --> Dodeli dostop do portala`, nato pa "
"odznačite potrditveno polje v stolpcu :guilabel:`Na portalu` in kliknete "
":guilabel:`Uporabi`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:74
msgid "Change portal username"
msgstr "Spreminjanje uporabniškega imena portala"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:76
msgid ""
"There may be times when a portal user wants to change their user login. This "
"can be done by any user in the database with administrator access rights. "
"The following process outlines the necessary steps to change the portal user "
"login."
msgstr ""
"Včasih želi uporabnik portala spremeniti svojo uporabniško prijavo. To lahko "
"naredi kateri koli uporabnik v zbirki podatkov z administratorskimi "
"pravicami dostopa. Naslednji postopek opisuje potrebne korake za spremembo "
"uporabniške prijave portala."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:81
msgid ""
":doc:`See the documentation on setting access rights </applications/general/"
"users/access_rights>`."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Oglejte si dokumentacijo o nastavitvi pravic dostopa </applications/"
"general/users/access_rights>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:84
msgid ""
"First, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users`. Then, "
"under :guilabel:`Filters`, select :guilabel:`Portal Users`, or "
"select :guilabel:`Add Custom Filter` and set the following "
"configuration :guilabel:`Groups` > :guilabel:`contains` > `portal`. After "
"making this selection, search for (and open) the portal user that needs to "
"be edited."
msgstr ""
"Najprej pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Nastavitve --> Uporabniki`. "
"Nato pod :guilabel:`Filtri` izberite :guilabel:`Uporabniki portala` ali "
"izberite :guilabel:`Dodaj filter po meri` in nastavite naslednjo "
"konfiguracijo :guilabel:`Skupine` > :guilabel:`vsebuje` > `portal`. Po tej "
"izbiri poiščite (in odprite) uporabnika portala, ki ga je treba urediti."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:89
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Edit` (if necessary), click into the :guilabel:`Email "
"Address` field, and proceed to make any necessary changes to this field. "
"The :guilabel:`Email Address` field is used to log into the Odoo portal."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi` (če je potrebno), kliknite v polje "
":guilabel:`E-poštni naslov` in nadaljujte z vsemi potrebnimi spremembami "
"tega polja. Polje :guilabel:`E-poštni naslov` se uporablja za prijavo v "
"portal Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:94
msgid ""
"Changing the :guilabel:`Email Address` (or login) only changes the "
"*username* on the customer's portal login."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje :guilabel:`E-poštnega naslova` (ali prijave) spremeni samo "
"*uporabniško ime* pri prijavi na portal stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:97
msgid ""
"In order to change the contact email, this change needs to take place on the "
"contact template in the *Contacts* app. Alternatively, the customer can "
"change their email directly from the portal, but the login **cannot** be "
"changed. :ref:`See change customer info <portal/custinfo>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti e-poštni naslov stika, mora ta sprememba potekati na "
"predlogi stika v aplikaciji *Stiki*. Druga možnost je, da stranka spremeni "
"svoj e-poštni naslov neposredno na portalu, vendar prijave **ni mogoče** "
"spremeniti. :ref:`Oglejte si spreminjanje informacij o stranki <portal/"
"custinfo>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:102
msgid "Customer portal changes"
msgstr "Spremembe na portalu za stranke"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:104
msgid ""
"There may be times when the customer would like to make changes to their "
"contact information, password/security, or payment information attached to "
"the portal account. This can be performed by the customer from their portal. "
"The following process is how a customer can change their contact information."
msgstr ""
"Včasih bi stranka rada spremenila svoje kontaktne podatke, geslo/varnost ali "
"plačilne podatke, povezane z računom portala. To lahko stranka izvede na "
"svojem portalu. Naslednji postopek prikazuje, kako lahko stranka spremeni "
"svoje kontaktne podatke."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:112
msgid "Change customer info"
msgstr "Spreminjanje informacij o stranki"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:114
msgid ""
"First enter the username and password (login) into the database login page "
"to access the portal user account. A portal dashboard will appear upon "
"successfully logging in. Portal documents from the various installed Odoo "
"applications will appear with the number count of each."
msgstr ""
"Najprej vnesite uporabniško ime in geslo (prijava) na prijavno stran baze "
"podatkov za dostop do uporabniškega računa portala. Po uspešni prijavi se bo "
"prikazala nadzorna plošča portala. Prikazani bodo dokumenti portala iz "
"različnih nameščenih aplikacij Odoo s številom posameznih dokumentov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:119
msgid ":ref:`Portal access documentation <portal/main>`."
msgstr ":ref:`Dokumentacija za dostop do portala <portal/main>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:121
msgid ""
"Next, navigate to the upper-right corner of the portal, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Edit` button, next to the :guilabel:`Details` section. Then, "
"change the pertinent information, and click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Nato pojdite v zgornji desni kot portala in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Uredi`, "
"poleg razdelka :guilabel:`Podrobnosti`. Nato spremenite ustrezne informacije "
"in kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:126
msgid "Change password"
msgstr "Spremeni geslo"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:128
#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:147
#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:166
msgid ""
"First enter the username and password (login) into the database login page "
"to access the portal user account. A portal dashboard will appear upon "
"successfully logging in."
msgstr ""
"Najprej vnesite uporabniško ime in geslo (prijava) na prijavno stran baze "
"podatkov za dostop do uporabniškega računa portala. Po uspešni prijavi se bo "
"prikazala nadzorna plošča portala."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:131
msgid ""
"If the customer would like to change their password for portal access, click "
"on the :guilabel:`Edit Security Settings` link, below the :guilabel:`Account "
"Security` section. Then, make the necessary changes, by typing in the "
"current :guilabel:`Password`, :guilabel:`New Password`, and verify the new "
"password. Lastly, click on :guilabel:`Change Password` to complete the "
"password change."
msgstr ""
"Če želi stranka spremeniti geslo za dostop do portala, kliknite povezavo "
":guilabel:`Uredi varnostne nastavitve`, pod razdelkom :guilabel:`Varnost "
"računa`. Nato naredite potrebne spremembe tako, da vnesete trenutno "
":guilabel:`Geslo`, :guilabel:`Novo geslo` in potrdite novo geslo. Na koncu "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Spremeni geslo`, da dokončate spremembo gesla."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:137
msgid ""
"If a customer would like to change the login, as documented above, contact "
"the Odoo database point-of-contact. :ref:`See above documentation on "
"changing the portal username <portal/login>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želi stranka spremeniti prijavo, kot je dokumentirano zgoraj, se obrnite "
"na kontaktno osebo baze podatkov Odoo. :ref:`Glejte zgornjo dokumentacijo o "
"spreminjanju uporabniškega imena portala <portal/login>`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:141
msgid ""
"Passwords for portal users and Odoo.com users remain separate, even if the "
"same email address is used."
msgstr ""
"Gesla za uporabnike portala in uporabnike Odoo.com ostanejo ločena, tudi če "
"je uporabljen enak e-poštni naslov."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:145
msgid "Add two-factor authentication"
msgstr "Dodaj dvofaktorsko preverjanje pristnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:150
msgid ""
"If the customer would like to turn on two-factor authentication (2FA) for "
"portal access, click on the :guilabel:`Edit Security Settings` link, below "
"the :guilabel:`Account Security` section."
msgstr ""
"Če želi stranka vklopiti dvofaktorsko preverjanje pristnosti (2FA) za dostop "
"do portala, kliknite povezavo :guilabel:`Uredi varnostne nastavitve`, pod "
"razdelkom :guilabel:`Varnost računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:153
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Enable two-factor authentication` to turn on :abbr:`2FA "
"(two-factor authentication)`. Confirm the current portal password in "
"the :guilabel:`Password` field. Then, click on :guilabel:`Confirm Password`. "
"Next, activate :abbr:`2FA (two-factor authentication)` in a :abbr:`2FA (two-"
"factor authentication)` app (Google Authenticator, Authy, etc.), by scanning "
"the :guilabel:`QR code` or entering a :guilabel:`Verification Code`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Omogoči dvofaktorsko preverjanje pristnosti`, da "
"vklopite :abbr:`2FA (dvofaktorsko preverjanje pristnosti)`. Potrdite "
"trenutno geslo portala v polju :guilabel:`Geslo`. Nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Potrdi geslo`. Nato aktivirajte :abbr:`2FA (dvofaktorsko "
"preverjanje pristnosti)` v aplikaciji :abbr:`2FA (dvofaktorsko preverjanje "
"pristnosti)` (Google Authenticator, Authy itd.) tako, da skenirate "
":guilabel:`kodo QR` ali vnesete :guilabel:`kodo za preverjanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:159
msgid ""
"Finally, click :guilabel:`Enable two-factor authentication` to complete the "
"setup."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu kliknite :guilabel:`Omogoči dvofaktorsko preverjanje pristnosti`, "
"da dokončate nastavitev."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:164
msgid "Change payment info"
msgstr "Spremeni podatke o plačilu"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/portal.rst:169
msgid ""
"If the customer would like to manage payment options, navigate to "
"the :guilabel:`Manage payment methods` in the menu on the right. Then, add "
"the new payment information, and select :guilabel:`Add new card`."
msgstr ""
"Če želi stranka upravljati možnosti plačila, pojdite na :guilabel:`Upravljaj "
"načine plačila` v meniju na desni. Nato dodajte nove podatke o plačilu in "
"izberite :guilabel:`Dodaj novo kartico`."

